hadiths[266]{hadithnumber,text}:
1,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis kaam ka main tumhen hukm dun, is par amal karo aur jis sey mana karun, us sey baaz raho."
2,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tak main tumhen ( kisi mamley mein azad ( chhodey rakhun , tab tak tum bhi mujhey chhodey rakho , ( bila wajeh sawal na karo) kyonkey tum sey pehley log apney anbiya (Alaihimussalam) sey sawalat karney aur) phir ( un ( key ehkam ( ki mukhalifat karney ki wajeh hi sey halak huye, lihaza jab main tumhen kisi kaam ka hukm dun to hasbe-himmat uski taameel karo aur jab kisi kaam sey mana kar dun to us sey ruk jao ."
3,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney meri itaat ki, usney Allah ki itaat ki aur jisney meri nafarmani ki usney Allah ki nafarmani ki."
4,"Hazrat Abu-Jafar Muhammad Baaqar (Rehmatullahi alaih) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey koi hadees suntey, to na is mein izafa kartey aur na kami kartey they."
5,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye, jabke hum faqr key barey mein guftgu kar rahey they aur us sey khof ka izhar kar rahey they, to aap ney farmaya : kya tum faqr sey dartey ho? qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum par duniya ( itni ziyada ( barsa di jaeygi, yahan tak key kisi key dil ko uskey siwa koi chiz maael nahin kereygi , (har shakhs uski taraf mutawajjeh ho jaeyga. ( Allah ki qism ! main tumhen roshan ( chaand ki raaton jaisi ( shariyat par chhod raha hun, jis key raat aur din barabar hain. 'Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sach farmaya. Allah ki qism ! aap hamen aisi roshan shariyat par chhod kar tashrif ley gaey hain, jis key raat aur din barabar hain."
6,"Hazrat Qurra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key eik giroh ko hamesha ( Allah Taala ki) madad hasil rahegi, un ki madad na karney wala unka kuch bigaad na sakeyga, yahan tak ki qiyamat qaaim ho jaey ."
7,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat mein sey eik giroh Allah key ehkam par hamesha puri tarah qaaim rahega , uski mukhalifat karney wala us ko nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakeyga ."
8,"Hazrat Abu Anba Kholani (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, ye wo ( Sabab ( hain jinhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath dono qiblon ki taraf namaz padhi hai. unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farmatey they : Allah Taala is Deen mein hamesha ( naey ( paudey lagata rahega aur un sey apni itaat mein kaam leta rahega ."
9,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) key walid Shuaib bin Muhammad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney khadey ho kar khutba diya aur) khutbey key doran mein) farmaya : tumharey ulama kahan hain? tumharey ulama kahan hain? mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap farmatey they : qiyamat qaaim na hogi magar meri ummat ki eik jamaat logon par ghalib rahegi, unhen koi parwa nahin hogi ke koi in ko zaleel o khuwar karey ya un ki madad kerey."
10,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat ki eik jamaat hamesha haq par qaaim rahegi aur uski madad ki jati rahegi, un ki mukhalifat karney waley unhen nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakengey, yahan tak key Allah Taala ka hukm ( qiyamat ( aa jaey ."
11,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik khat khincha, (phir (uski daain taraf do khat kheenchey aur baain taraf bhi do khat kheenchey. phir darmiyan waley khat par haath rakh kar farmaya : ye Allah ka raasta hai.  phir ye aayat tilawat farmaee : (وَاَنَّ ھٰذَا صِرَاطِيْ مُسْتَقِـيْمًا)  aur ye mera raasta hai sidha , lihaza iski perwi karo, aur  dusri (raahon par na chalo, warna wo tumhen us (Allah (ki raah sey door kar dengi))."
12,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Madi Karb Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : anqarib (aisa zamana aaney wala hai ke) aadmi apney takht par tek lagaey betha hoga, usey meri koi hadees sunai jaeygi to kaheyga : hamarey aur tumharey darmiyan (faisla karney wali) Allah ki kitab hai. hamen is mein jo chiz halal milegi , usey halal manengey , aur jo chiz is mein haram paeyngey , hum usey haram qarar dengey. sun lo ! jo kuchh Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney haram farmaya , wo bhi isi tarah haram hai jis tarah Allah ka haram kiya huwa ."
13,"Hazrat abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tum mein sey kisi ko is haal mein na paon ke wo palang par tek lagaey betha ho, usey merey ehkam mein sey koi hukm ya mumaniat pahunchey aur wo keh dey : main nahin janta , hum jo kuch Allah ki kitab mein paeyngey, uski perwi kerengey ."
14,"Hazrat ummul-mominin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs hamarey Deen mein wo chiz ejaad karey jo ( asal mein) us mein) shamil ) nahin hai, to wo mardud hai."
15,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik Ansari aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) key khilaf Harra ki un barsati nadiyon key mutalliq dawa pesh kya, jin sey wo khajuron ( key baghaat ( ko sairab kartey they. Ansari ney kaha : pani chhod do ke guzar kar) merey khet mein) aa jaey . Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney inkar kar diya . dono apna jhagda Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey, to aap ney farmaya : Zuber ! (apney baagh ko) sinch kar apney padosi key liye pani chhod diya karo . Ansari ney nagawari ka izhar kya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (aap ney ye faisla (isliye) kya hai) ke wo aap ki phuphi ka beta hai. ( ye sun kar) Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Chehrey Mubarak ka rang badal gaya . phir farmaya : Zuber ! baagh ko pani do , phir pani ko rokey rakho yahan tak key munderon tak pahunch jaey (aur baagh khub sairab ho jaey .) Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! merey khayal main to ye aayat usi barey mein nazil hui hai : ( فَلَا وَ رَبِّكَ . . يُسَلِّمُوْا تَسْلِــيْمًا )' qism hai aap key rab ki ! ye momin nahin ho saktey jab tak ke apney bahami (aapsi) ikhtilaf mein aap ko munsif na maan lein , phir aap key faisley par dil mein koi nagawari bhi mehsus na karen, aur (usey) puri tarah taslim kar lein."
16,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki bandiyon ko masjid mein namaz padhney sey mana na karo . ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) key eik betey ney kaha : hum to unhen mana kerengey . Salim (Rahimahullah) bayan farmatey hain ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sakht naraz huye aur farmaya : main tujhey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees sunata hun aur to kehta hai hum to mana kerengey ."
17,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unka eik bhatija unkey paas betha huwa tha. usney (do ungliyon key darmiyan rakh kar door) kankari phenki, to unhoney usey mana kiya aur kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is harkat sey mana kiya hai aur farmaya hai : is sey shikar hota hai na dushman zakhmi hota hai (yani koi faeyda nahin, lekin (ye kisi ka) hadsati tor par (daant tod deti hai aur) kisi ki (aankh phod deti hai). (kuchh der baad) unkey bhatijey ney phir yehi harkat ki to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main tujhey bata raha hun ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is sey mana farmaya hai, to phir bhi ye harkat karta hai, main tujh sey kabhi kalam nahin karunga."
18,"Hazrat Qabisa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba Hazrat Ubada bin Samit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ney, jo (baiat Aqba mein) ansaar key numaaindey they, Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein Rome key ilaqey mein jihad kiya. (wahan) unhoney dekha ke log soney ki daliyon key badley dinaaron ka aur chaandi ki daliyon key badley dirahmon ka lein dain kar rahey hain. Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : logo ! tum to sood kha rahey ho. mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey suna hai, 'soney ko soney key badley na becho magar barabar barabar, na is mein ziyadti ho na udhaar. Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : abul-Waleed ! merey khayal mein sood wohi hai jis mein udhaar ho. Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main aap ko Allah key Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka farman sunata hun aur aap mujhey apni raey batatey hain, agar Allah Taala mujhey (us jihad sey sahih salaamat) wapis ley gaya to main us ilaqey mein nahin rahunga jahan mujh par aap ki hukumat ho. jab wo jihad sey wapis huye to (Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Sham janey key bajaey) Madina ja pahunchey, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Abul-Waleed ! aap yahan kyon tashrif ley aaye? Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney waqia bayan farmaya aur Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key sath rehney key barey mein jo kuchh kaha tha, wo bhi bayan farmaya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Abul-Waleed ! apney ilaqey mein wapis chaley jaaiye, Allah bura karey us ilaqey ka, jis mein aap aur aap jaisey afrad na hon. aur Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko likh bheja : Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) par aap ki koi hukumat nahin aur Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney jo kuchh kaha hai, logon sey usi key mutabiq amal karao, kyonkey (shariyat ka) hukm yehi hai."
19,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab main tumhen Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki koi hadees sunaun to tum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key barey mein wo guman rakho jo ziyada behtar aur hidayat o taqwa sey qarib tar ho."
20,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab main tumhen Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki koi hadees sunaun to tum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key barey mein wo guman rakho , jo ziyada behtar aur hidayat o taqwa sey qarib tar ho."
21,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey ilm mein ye baat nahin aani chahiye (us sey ijtinab karo) ke tum mein sey kisi ko meri hadees sunai jaey aur wo apney palang par tek lagaey betha ho aur (meri hadees sun kar) keh dey : Quran padho. (baat ye hai ke) jo bhi achi baat kahi gaee hai wo mainey kahi hai.'"
22,"Hazrat abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik aadmi sey kaha : bhatijey ! jab main tumhen Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki koi hadees sunaun to uskey muqabley mein misalen na bayan kya karo . jo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai, Imam Ibne-Maja ney yahan usi hadees ki eik aur sanad bhi bayan ki hai, hadees key alfaz dobara zikr nahin kiye ."
23,"Hazrat Amr bin Memun (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke main har Jumerat ko bila nagha din dhaley Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hota tha, mainey unhen kabhi ye kehtey nahin suna ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney yun farmaya hai. eik din unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya. padhi. (uskey baad) sar jhuka liya (khamosh ho gaey) mainey aap ki taraf nazar uthai to dekha ke wo qamis key batan kholey khadey hain, aankhen bhar aai hain aur ragein phool gaee hain (hadees bayan karney ki himmat nahin ho rahi) aakhir farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney yehi irshad farmaya tha, ya is sey kam aur besh ya is sey qarib ya us sey miltey jaltey alfaz farmaai they."
24,"Imam Muhammad bin Sirin (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki koi hadees bayan farmatey , to us ko mukammal karney key baad farmatey : ( اٴَوْ کَمَا قَالَ رَسُوْلُ اللہِ (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , ya jis tarah Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya."
25,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey arz kya ke hamen Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadisein sunaaiye . unhoney farmaya : hum boodhey ho gaey hain aur bhoolney lagey hain jabke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees bayan karna bahut mushkil kaam hai."
26,"Imam Shaaby (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main saal bhar Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ki majlis mein hazir raha , (us doran mein) mainey unhen kabhi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey koi chiz bayan kartey nahin suna ."
27,"Hazrat Taaus (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey suna , unhoney farmaya : hum hadeesein yad kiya kartey they aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadeesein yad ki jati hain, lekin jab tum ney sakht aur naram zamin par chalna shuru kar diya to (tum par aitimaad) door ki baat hai."
28,"Hazrat Qarza bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamein koofa rawana farmaya aur hamein rukhsat kiya. (us moqe par) aap hamarey sath chaltey chaltey maqam,  siraar tak pahunch gaey. tab farmaya : kya tumhen malum hai ke main kyon tumharey sath chal kar aaya hun? hamney arz kiya : (hamarey) as-haabe Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) honey ka haq samajhtey huye aur ansaar key haq (ki adaegi) key khayal sey. farmaya : balke main to isliye tumharey sath chal kar aaya hun ke main tum sey eik baat kehna chahta tha. mainey chaha ke merey is chalney ki wajeh sey tum usey yad rakho. (taake tumhen yad rahey ke ye wo aham nasihat hai jo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Madina sey itni door hamarey sath aa kar hamein ki thi.) tum aisey logon key paas ja rahey ho jinkey seeney Quran ki wajeh sey is tarah josh maar rahey hain jis tarah handiyaa ubalti hai, jab wo tumhen dekhengey to gardanen utha kar tumhari taraf mutawajjeh hongey aur kahengey : ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sathi hain. to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadisein kam bayan karna, (jab tum is par amal karogey) to phir main bhi (ajr mein) tumhara shareek hunga."
29,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazeed (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Madina Munawra sey Makka Mukarrama tak Hazrat Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka hum safar raha. (purey safar mein) mainey aap ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey eik hadees bhi riwayat kartey nahin suna ."
30,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney jaan-bujh kar mujh par jhoot baandha , usey chahiye ke (jahannam ki) aag mein apna thikana bana ley ."
31,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujh par jhoot na baandho , jhooti baat merey zimmey lagana aag ( jahannam) mein dakhil kar deta hai."
32,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney mujh par jhoot bola . mera guman hai aap ney ye bhi farmaya : jaan-bujh kar . to usey chahiye ke (jahannam ki) aag mein apna thikana bana ley."
33,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney mujh par jhoot bola , usey chahiye ke apna thikana ( jahannam ki) aag mein bana ley ."
34,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney merey zimmey wo baat lagai jo mainey nahin kahi , usey chahiye ke apna thikana ( jahannam ki) aag mein bana ley ."
35,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko us member par ye farmatey suna hai : mujh sey b-kasrat hadisein bayan na karo aur jo shakhs meri taraf mansub kar key koi baat kahey , wo haq sach baat kahey , jisney meri taraf nisbat kar key wo baat kahi , jo mainey nahin kahi usey chahiye ke apna thikana ( jahannam ki) aag mein bana ley ."
36,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey (apney walid) Hazrat Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) sey arz kya : kya wajeh hai ke main aap ko Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey is tarah hadisein bayan kartey nahin sunta jis tarah ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) aur falan falan Sabab ko sunta hun? farmaya : mainey jab sey Islam qubul kya hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey) aap ki wafat tak kabhi ( juda nahin huwa , lekin mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey eik kalma suna hai) jiski wajeh sey riwayat hadees sey ijtinab karta hun (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : jisney mujh par qasdan jhoot bola , usey chahiye ke apna thikana ( jahannam ki) aag mein bana ley ."
37,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney mujh par qasdan jhoot bola , usey chahiye ke apna thikana aag mein bana ley ."
38,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney meri taraf nisbat kar key koi hadees bayan ki, halanke uskey khayal mein wo jhoot hai to wo bhi do jhooton mein sey eik jhoota hai."
39,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs mujh sey koi hadees bayan karta hai aur uskey khayal mein wo jhoot hai, wo bhi jhoot bolney waley do afrad mein sey eik hai."
40,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs mujh sey koi hadees riwayat karta hai aur uskey ilm key mutabiq wo jhoot hai to wo bhi jhoot bolney waley do afrad mein sey eik hai.' Muhammad bin Abdullah bayan kartey hain ke hamen Janab Hasan bin Musa ney Shoba sey Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ki misl hadees bayan ki."
41,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs meri taraf mansub kar key koi hadees bayan karta hai aur uskey ilm key mutabiq wo jhoot hai to wo bhi jhoot bolney waley do afrad mein sey eik hai.'"
42,"Hazrat Arbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hum logon mein khadey huye aur eik mutassir kun waaz farmaya, jis sey dil (Allah ki narazi aur azab sey) khof zada ho gaey aur aankhen aasuon se bhar gaeen. arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney hamein aisey nasihat farmaai hai jis tarah rukhsat karney wala nasihat kiya karta hai, aap hum sey koi ehad-o-paimaan ley lijiye. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karo aur hukm sun kar taameel karo agar-che (tumhara haakim) koi Habshi ghulam ho. aur tum merey baad sakht ikhtilaf dekhogey, to meri sunnat ko aur hidayat yafta Khulfaae Raashdeen key tareeqey ko ikhtiyar karna, usey dadhon sey pakad kar rakhna, (us par mazbooti sey qaaim rehna) aur naey naey kamon sey perhez karna, kyonkey har bidat gumrahi hai."
43,"Hazrat Arbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein (aisa) waaz farmaya, jis key asar sey aakhon sey aansu behney lagey aur dil (Allah ki narazi aur azab sey) khof-zada ho gaey. hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye to aisa waaz hai jaisey kisi rukhsat karney waley ki nasihat , to aap hum sey kya wada letey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tumhen roshan (shariyat) par chhod raha hun. jiski raat bhi din ki tarah (roshan) hai, merey baad wohi shakhs tedh ikhtiyar kerega jo halak honey wala hai. tum mein sey jo koi zinda rahega , wo jald bahut ikhtilaf dekhega , lihaza tumhen meri sunnat aur hidayat yafta khulafae-Rashidin ka jo tariqa malum ho usi ko ikhtiyar karna. usey dadhon key sath mazbooti sey pakadna. aur (ameer ki) itaat ko lazim pakadna agar-che wo Habshi ghulam ho kyonkey momin to nakel waley oont ki tarah hota hai jahan ley jaya jaey, chala jata hai."
44,"Hazrat Arbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen subh ki namaz padhaai , phir chehra Mubarak hamari taraf pher liya aur eik pur-taseer wa'z farmaya. uskey baad Raavi ney puri hadees bayan ki."
45,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab khutba irshad farmatey to aap ki aankhen surkh ho jatin , aawaz buland ho jati aur ghussa tez ho jata. (yun mehsus hota) goya aap (dushman key) lashkar sey khof dilatey huye keh rahey hain : wo subh ya Sham ko hamla aawar honey wala hai aur aap apni shahadat ki ungli aur darmiyani ungli ko mila kar farmatey : mujhey aur qiyamat ko is tarah bheja gaya hai jis tarah do ungliyan (eik doosrey sey bahut qarib hain.) iskey ilawa farmatey : amma baad! behtareen chiz Allah ki kitab hai, aur behtareen tariqa Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka tariqa hai. aur bad-tareen kaam naey ejaad karda kaam (bidatein) hain aur har bidat gumrahi hai. aur farmatey they : jo shakhs ( martey waqt) maal chhod jaey, wo uskey ghar walon ka hai aur jo (apney zimmey) qarz chhod jaey ya biwi bachon ko (laawaaris) chhod jaey to (uski adaeygi aur un ki kafalat) merey zimmey hai.'"
46,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : cheezen do hi hain : kalam aur amali tareeqa, to behtareen kalamullah ka kalam hai aur behtareen tariqa Muhammad  (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka tariqa hai. khabrdar ! naey naey kamon sey bacho , sab sey burey kaam wo hain jo ( Deen mein) naey ejaad kiye gaey hon aur har nau-ejaad amal bidat hai aur har bidat gumrahi hai. khabrdar ! tum mein lambi zindagi ka khayal paida na ho jaey warna tumharey dil sakht ho jaeyngey. khabrdar ! jo kuchh aaney wala hai wo qarib hi hai, door to wo hai jo aaney wala nahin . khabrdar ! bad nasib wo hai jo maa key pet mein bad-naseeb qarar paa gaya aur khush nasib wo hai jisney dusron (key burey anjam) sey nasihat hasil kar li. khabrdar ! momin sey jang karna kufr hai aur usey gaali dena fisq (nafarmaani) hai. kisi musalman key liye halal nahin ke teen din sey ziyada apney (musalman) bhai sey qata' talluq kiye rahey. khabrdar ! jhoot sey bacho, jhoot na sanjeedagi sey bolna jayez hai aur na mazaq mein. aisa nahin hona chahiye ke aadmi apney bachchey sey koi wada karey phir usey pura na kerey. bila-shubha jhoot gunah ki taraf ley jata hai aur gunah jahannam ki taraf ley jata hai aur sach neki ki raah dikhata hai aur neki jannat mein ley jati hai. sachchey key barey mein kaha jata hai : usney sach bola aur neki ka kaam kiya aur jhootey ko kaha jata hai : usney jhoot bola aur gunah ka irtikab kiya. khabrdar ! (baaz oqaat aisa bhi hota hai ke) banda jhoot boltaa rehta hai yahan tak ke Allah key yhaan usey kazaab (jhuta) likh diya jata hai."
47,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (ھُوَ الَّذِيْ اَنْزَلَ عَلَيْكَ الْكِتٰبَ مِنْهُ اٰيٰتٌ مُّحْكَمٰتٌ ھُنَّ اُمُّ الْكِتٰبِ وَ اُخَرُ مُتَشٰبِهٰتٌ . . . وَمَا يَذَّكَّرُ اِلَّا اُولُوا الْاَلْبَابِ) wohi hai jisney aap par kitab nazil ki, uski kuchh aayaat mohkam (mazboot)  (wazeh) hain, jo is kitab ki asal hain aur kuchh dusri mutshabihaat (ghair wazeh) hain, to jinkey dilon mein tedh hai wo mutshabihaat key peechhey padey rehtey hain. jo mutashabeh (ghair wazeh) hain, unka maqsad mehaz fitney aur taaweel ki talash hota hai, halanke un ki asal haqiqat sey Allah key siwa koi waqif nahin aur ilm mein pukhtagi rakhney waley kehtey hain : hamara un (mutshabihaat)  par eman hai, ye sab hamarey rab ki taraf sey hain aur nasihat to aql mand hi hasil kartey hain.  phir farmaya : aey Aaisha ! jab tum un logon ko dekho jo in (mutshabihaat) key barey mein behes kartey hain to (jaan lo ke) yehi wo log hain jinhein Allah ney (is aayat mein) murad liya hai, lihaza un sey bacho."
48,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kuch log hidayat par they, phir uskey baad gumrahi ikhtiyar kar li to unhen jhagdey hi nasib huye . phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ( بَلْ هُمْ قَوْمٌ خَصِمُونَ )' balke yehi log jhagdalu hain."
49,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala bid'ati ka roza qubul karta hai na namaz , na sadqa , na Haj , na Umra , na jihad , na nafl , na farz . wo Islam sey is tarah nikal jata hai jis tarah goondhey huye aatey mein sey baal nikal jata hai."
50,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney bid'ati ka amal qubul karney sey inkar kar diya hai yahan tak ke wo shakhs bidat tarak kar dey ."
51,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs batil par hotey huye jhagda tarak kar dey , uskey liye jannat key atraaf main eik mehal tayyar kya jaeyga aur jo shakhs haq par hotey huye jhagda tarak kar dey , uskey liye jannat key beech mein) mehal ( tayyar kya jaeyga aur jo shakhs apney akhlaq achey kar ley , uskey liye ( jannat key ( buland tareen hissey mein mehal tayyar kya jaeyga."
52,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ilm ko is tarah nahin uthaeyga ke usey logon key dilon sey salb kar ley , balke wo ulama ko faut kar key ilm ko uthaeyga . jab koi aalim baqi nahin rahega to log jahil sardar muqarrar kar leingey , phir un sey (masaayel) puchey jaeyngey to wo ilm key baghair fatwey dengey . (is tarah khud) gumrah hongey , aur dusron ko bhi gumrah kerengey ."
53,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ko baghair daleel key fatwa diya gaya (aur usney us ghalat fatwa par amal kar liya) to uska gunah is par hai jisney usey fatwa diya ."
54,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ilm teen cheezen hain, aur jo kuch unkey ilawa hai wo izafi hai (uskey baghair guzaara ho sakta hai.) mohkam aayaat, Sabit shuda sunnatein aur maali huquq jo adl par mabni hon."
55,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jab mujhey Yamen bheja to farmaya : tum hergiz faisla na karna magar (yaqeeni) ilm key mutabiq aur agar kisi mamley mein mushkil pad jaey to twaqquf karna (thehar jana) yahan tak ke (soorate haal) wazeh tor par samajh ley (aur tehqiq kar ley) ya uskey barey mein mujhey likh dena."
56,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : Bani-Israel ka maamla durust raha yahan tak ke un mein dusri qomon ki laundiyon ki aulad paida ho gaee. (badey ho kar) unhoney apni raey sey masaayel bayan kiye , to wo gumrah huye aur (doosron ko bhi) gumrah kya.'"
57,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eman key saath ya sattar sey ziyada shobey hain. un mein sab sey maamuli (kam tar darja) raastey sey takleef deh chiz ka door karna hai aur sab sey buland ( لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللهُ) kehna hai aur haya bhi eman ki eik shaakh hai. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey yehi riwayat eik dusri sanad sey bhi marvi hai."
58,"Hazrat Salim (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat ki, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko suna ke wo apney bhai ko haya key mutalliq nasihat kar raha tha to aap ney (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : beshak haya eman ki eik shaakh hai."
59,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key dil mein raai key daney barabar bhi takabbur hoga, wo jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga aur jis key dil mein raai key daney barabar bhi eman hoga wo aag (jahannam) mein dakhil nahin hoga ."
60,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Allah Taala (qiyamat key din) mominon ko jahannam sey najat dey dega aur wo aman mein ho jaeyngey to phir wo apney un bhaiyon key barey mein jo (gunahon ki kasrat ki wajeh sey) jahannam mein chaley gaey, is qadr israr sey apney Rab sey bar-bar arz kerengey ke duniya mein apney bhai sey apney haq key liye is tarah jhagda na kiya hoga. wo kahengey : aey hamarey parwardigar ! ye hamarey bhai hain, hamarey sath namazein padha kartey they, hamarey sath rozey rakha kartey they, hamarey sath haj kartey they, tu ney unhen (apney adl ki bina par) jahannam mein dakhil kar diya (ab apney Fazal sey unhen maaf farma dey).  Allah Taala farmaeyga : jao , jinhen tum pehchantey ho (jahannam sey) nikal lo. wo un (dozakhiyon) key paas ayengey aur unhen un ki shaklon sey pehchan leingey. aag un ki soorten nahin khayegi (chehrey nahin jalengey), aag ney kisi ko aadhi pindliyon tak jala diya hoga, kisi ko takhnon tak jala diya hoga, wo unhein nikal laeyngey aur arz kerengey : aey hamarey Rab ! jinka tu ney hamein hukm diya tha, unhen hamney nikal liya hai. Allah Taala phir farmaeyga : jis key dil main eik Dinar key wazan barabar eman hai usey bhi nikal lo, phir (irshad hoga) jis key dil mein nisf (aadhe) Dinar key wazan barabar (emaan hai, usey bhi nikal lo) uskey baad (yahan tak hukm ho jaeyga ke) jis key dil mein raai key daney barabar eman hai (usey bhi jahannam sey nikal lo). Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jisey yaqin na aaye wo is aayat ko padh ley : ( اِنَّ اللّٰهَ لَا يَظْلِمُ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ padhi. وَ اِنْ تَكُ حَسَـنَةً يُّضٰعِفْھَا وَ يُؤْتِ مِنْ لَّدُنْهُ اَجْرًا عَظِيْمًا )''be shak Allah Taala zarra barabar bhi zulm nahin karta, aur agar (kisi ki) koi neki hogi to usey kaee guna badha dega aur usey apney paas sey ajre-azeem ata farmaeyga.''"
61,"Hazrat Jundub bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sath nasib huwa jabke hum bharpur jawan they, to hamney Quran ka ilm hasil karney sey pehley eman seekha , phir hamney Quran seekha to us sey hamarey eman mein izafa ho gaya ."
62,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat ki do jamaaten aisi hain, jinka Islam mein koi hissey nahin : ( مُرْجِئَہ ) aur ( قَدَرِیَّہ )."
63,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bethey they ke eik aadmi aaya jis key kapdey intehai safed aur sar key baal intehai siyah they, is par safar key asraat (gardo-ghubar aur thakan waghera) nazar nahin aa rahey they aur usey hum mein sey koi pehchanta nahin tha. wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar beth gaya, apney ghutney aap key ghutnon sey mila diye aur apney haath apni raanon par rakh liye , phir usney kaha : aey Muhammad ! Islam kiya hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is baat ki gawahi dena ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main (Muhammad) Allah ka Rasool hun, namaz qaaim karna , zakat dena , Ramzan key rozey rakhna aur Baitullah ka Haj karna. usney kaha : aap ney sach farmaya. hamein is par tajjub huwa ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal karta hai aur (khud hi) tasdeeq bhi karta hai (ke aap ka jawab sahih hai), phir usney kaha : aey Muhammad ! eman kya hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (emaan ye hai ke) to Allah par, uskey farishton par , uskey Rasulon par , uski kitabon par , qiyamat par aur achchi buri taqdir par eman laye. usney kaha : aap ney sach farmaya. hamein is par tajjub huwa ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal bhi karta hai aur aap ki tasdeeq bhi karta hai, phir usney kaha : aey Muhammad ! ehsan kya hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (ehsan ye hai ke) to Allah ki ibadat is tarah karey goya to usey dekh raha hai, agar to usey nahin dekhta to wo to tujhey dekhta hai.  usney kaha : qiyamat kab aayegi? aap ney farmaya, ''jis sey uskey mutalliq puchha ja raha hai, wo poochhney waley sey ziyada nahin janta.'' usney kaha : uski alamat kya hai? aap ney farmaya : (qurb qiyamat ki alamaten ye hain) londi apni maalika ko janeygi. Wakee (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : yani ajam (ghair arab) ki aurton sey Arbon ki aulad hogi. aur ye ke tum aisey logon ko dekhogey jinkey pairon mein jootiyaan nahin, jism par kapdey nahin, muflis hain (khaney ko khurak nahin) bakriyan charatey hain, (lekin phir unkey paas itni dolat aa jaeygi ke) eik doosrey sey badh kar badi badi imaraten banaeyngey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : teen din baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujh sey miley to farmaya : kya tum ko malum hai wo aadmi kon tha?   mainey arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool ko ziyada malum hai. aap ney farmaya : wo Jibril (Alaihissalam) they, tum logon ko tumharey Deen ki aham baaten sikhaaney aaye they.   Abdullah bin Yazeed ney isi key misl (jaisi) riwayat eik dusri sanad sey bayan ki hai."
64,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar logon mein tashrif farma they ke eik shakhs khidmat aqdas mein hazir huwa aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! eman kya hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( eman ye hai) ke to Allah par , uskey farishton par , uski kitabon par , uskey Rasulon par aur us sey mulaqat par eman laye aur dobara zinda honey par bhi eman laye . usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Islam kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to Allah ki ibadat karey aur uskey sath kisi ko shareek na karey , farz namaz qaaim karey , farz ka ada karey aur Ramzan key rozey rakhey. , usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ehsan kya hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to Allah ki ibadat is tarah karey goya to usey dekh raha hai, agar to usey nahin dekhta to wo tujhey dekhta hai. usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! qiyamat kab aayegi ? aap ney farmaya : jis sey uskey mutalliq puchha ja raha hai, wo poochhney waley sey ziyada nahin janta lekin main tujhey uski alamaten batata hun . jab londi apni maalika ko janegi to ye uski eik alamat hai, jab bakriyon key charwahey eik doosrey key muqabley mein lambi chodi imaraten banaeyn to ye bhi uski alamat hai, ( lekin uskey waqt ka ta'yun) un paanch chizon mein shamil hai jinhen Allah key siwa koi nahin janta , phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (نَّ اللَّـهَ عِندَهُ عِلْمُ السَّاعَةِ وَيُنَزِّلُ الْغَيْثَ وَيَعْلَمُ ما في الْأَرْحَامِ padhi. وَمَا تَدْرِي نَفْسٌ مَّاذَا تَكْسِبُ ग़दन padhi. وَمَا تَدْرِي نَفْسٌ بِأَيِّ أَرْضٍ تَمُوتُ padhi. نَّ اللَّـهَ عَلِيمٌ خَبِيرٌ) qiyamat ka ilm Allah hi key paas hai, wo barish nazil karta hai aur wohi janta hai ke (mada key) rahmon mein kya hai aur kisi ko malum nahin ke wo kal kya kamaeyga aur kisi ko malum nahin ke us ko kis zamin mein maut aayegi , yaqinan Allah Taala ilm rakhney wala ba-khabar hai.'"
65,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eman naam hai dil sey) Allah ki) Maarifat ka, zaban sey iqrar aur) jism key ( aaza key sath ( uskey mutabiq) amal karney ka . Abu-Salat ney kaha : agar ye sanad kisi majnun par padhi jaey to wo tandurust ho jaey ."
66,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs us waqt tak momin nahin ho sakta jab tak apney ( musalman ( bhai key liye . ya farmaya : apney hamsaaey key liye bhi wo chiz pasand na karey jo apney liye pasand karta hai.'
67,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs eman daar nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke main usey uski aulad, walid aur tamam logon sey ziyada mehbub ho jaun."
68,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum jannat mein dakhil nahin hogey jab tak momin na bin jao aur (kamil) momin nahin bin saktey jab tak baham (aapas mein) mohabbat karney waley na bin jao . kya main tumhen wo kaam na bataun jis key karney sey tumharey andar eik doosrey ki mohabbat paida ho jaey ? aapas mein, 'salam,' ko riwaaj do."
69,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena gunah hai aur us sey jang karna kufr hai."
70,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eik Allah key liye khulus rakhtey huye aur kisi ko uska shareek na maan kar sirf uski ibadat kartey huye, namaz padhtey aur Zakat detey huye duniya sey rukhsat huwa, uski maut us haal mein aati hai ke Allah us sey razi hota hai. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ka Deen yehi hai jisey Rasool ley kar aaye aur jisey unhoney apney rab ki taraf sey (bandon ko) pahunchaya, baad mein (sachi jhooti) baaten khalat-malat ho gaeen aur tarah tarah ki man marzi ki baaten samney aa gaeen. uski tasdeeq Allah ki kitab ki in aayaat sey hoti hai jo aakhir mein nazil huin. Allah Taala ka irshad hai : ( فَإِنْ تَابُوا ) ''pas agar wo tauba keren.'' Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : yani buton sey dast kaash! ho jaeyn (chod de) aur un ki ibadat tarak kar den. (وَأَقَامُوا الصَّلَاةَ وَآتَوُا الزَّكَاةَ )''aur namaz qaaim karen aur zakat ada keren.'' doosri aayat mein farmaya : ( فَإِنْ تَابُوا وَأَقَامُوا الصَّلَاةَ وَآتَوُا الزَّكَاةَ فَإِخْوَانُكُمْ فِي الدِّينِ)''agar wo tauba kar lein, namaz qaaim karen aur zakat ada karen to wo bhi tumharey deeni bhai hain.'' Abu Hatim ney Ubedullah bin Musa sey unhoney Abu-Jafar Al Raazi sey, unhoney Rabee bin Anas sey isi mafhoom ki eik mursal riwayat bayan ki."
71,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke logon sey jihad karun yahan tak ke wo gawahi den ke Allah key siwa koi mabood haqeeqi nahin aur main (Muhammad) Allah ka Rasool hun aur namaz qaaim karen aur Zakat ada karen ."
72,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey jihad karun yahan tak ke wo gawahi den ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main (Muhammad) Allah ka Rasool hun, aur namaz qaaim karen aur zakat ada karen ."
73,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas aur Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat mein sey do jamaaten aisi hain jinka Islam mein koi hissey nahin Marjiya aur Qadriya.
74,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, un dono ney farmaya : eman mein izafa aur kami hoti hai."
75,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eman badhta aur ghat-ta hai."
76,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hadees sunai wo ( khud bhi) sachchey they, aur unhen (Allah ki taraf sey bhi) sachi khabar mili. (aap ney farmaya : )   insan ka maadha banaya uski maa key pet mein chaalis din (qatrey ki surat mein) jama rehta hai, phir itni hi muddat key liye (jamey huye khoon ki) phutki ya loathra bin jata hai, phir itna hi arsa gosht ka tukda bana rehta hai, phir Allah Taala uskey paas eik farishta bhejta hai jisey chaar baaton (key likhney) ka hukm diya jata hai. Allah Taala farmata hai : uskey aemal, uski umr aur uska rizq likh dey aur ye bhi ke wo bad-qismat hoga ya khush-qismat. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! eik aadmi jannatiyon waley amal karta rehta hai yahan tak ke uskey aur jannat key darmiyan eik haath ka fasla reh jata hai, phir is par (taqdir ki) tehreer ghalib aa jati hai aur wo jahannamiyon wala amal kar key jahannam mein dakhil ho jata hai. (isi tarah) eik aadmi jahannamiyon waley amal karta rehta hai yahan tak ke wo jahannam sey eik haath door reh jata hai, phir is par (taqdir ka)  likha ghalib aa jata hai, chunanche wo jannatiyon wala amal kar key jannat mein dakhil ho jata hai."
77,"Ibne-Delmi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : merey dil mein taqdir key masley mein shubha paida huwa , jis sey mujhey khatra mehsus huwa ke kahin wo mera Deen aur kaam (maamlat) tabah na kar dey , chunanche main Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . mainey kaha : Abu-Munzir ! merey dil mein taqdir key barey mein shubha paida ho gaya hai, jis sey mujhey apney aur maamlat key barey mein (kharabi ka) khof hai. mujhey uskey mutalliq kuch farmaiye, shayad us sey Allah Taala mujhey faeyda bakhsh dey . Hazrat abi (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : agar Allah Taala (tamam) aasmano walon aur (tamam) zamin walon ko azab dena chahey to dey sakta hai. ye uska un par zulm nahin hoga . aur agar un par rehmat karey to uski rehmat unkey aamal sey behtar hogi . aur agar terey paas Uhad pahad jitna sona ho ya Uhad pahad jitna maal ho aur to usey Allah ki raah mein kharch kar dey , to tera ye amal qubul nahin hoga jab tak ke to taqdir par eman na laye . tujhey malum hona chahiye jo musibat tujhey pahunchi hai wo tujh sey talney wali na thi ( usey bahar haal aana hi tha) aur jo musibat tujhey nahin pahunchi wo tujhey pahunchney wali na thi aur (ye jaan ley ke) agar teri maut us aqidey key siwa kisi aur aqidey par hui to to jahannam mein dakhil hoga. aur agar to merey bhai Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ja kar ye masla poochh ley to koi harj nahin. chunanche Ibne-Delmi (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey ye masla poochha, unhoney bhi wohi baat farmaai jo Ubai (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaai thi . aur farmaya : agar to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas jaey (aur masla daryaft kerey) to koi harj nahin . chunanche main Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey puchha , unhoney wohi baat farmaai jo doosrey dono hazraat ney farmaai thi . aur farmaya : Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ja kar un sey poochh lo . phir main Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey masla puchha . unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna hai, aap ney farmaya : agar Allah Taala ( tamam ( aasmano walon aur) tamam ( zamin walon ko azab dena chahey to dey sakta hai. ye uska un par zulm nahin hoga . aur agar un par rehmat karey to uski rehmat unkey aamal sey behtar hogi . aur agar terey paas Uhad pahad jitna sona ho ya ahad pahad jitna maal ho aur to usey Allah ki raah mein kharch kar dey , to tera ye amal qubul nahin kerega yahan tak ke to sari taqdir par eman laye, aur (yaqeen key sath) jaan ley ke jo musibat tujhey pahunchi hai wo tujh sey talney wali na thi aur jo musibat tujhey nahin pahunchi , wo tujhey pahunchney wali na thi . aur (jaan ley ke) agar teri maut us aqidey key siwa kisi aur aqidey par hui to to jahannam mein dakhil hoga . aur agar to merey bhai Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ja kar ye masla poochh ley to koi harj nahin . chunanche Ibne-Delmi (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain, main Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey ye masla puchha , unhoney bhi wohi baat farmaai jo Hazrat abi (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaai thi. aur farmaya : agar to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas jaey (aur masla daryaft karey ( to koi harj nahin . chunanche main Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey puchha , unhoney wohi baat farmaai jo doosrey dono hazraat ney farmaai thi . aur farmaya : Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ja kar un sey poochh lo . phir main Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey masla puchha . unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna hai, aap ney farmaya : agar Allah ta'ala (tamam) aasmano walon aur (sab) zamin walon ko azab dena chahey to dey sakta hai, ye uska un par zulm nahin hoga aur agar un par rehmat karey to uski rehmat unkey aamal sey behtar hogi. aur agar terey paas Uhad jitna sona ho ya ahad pahad jitna sona ho aur to usey Allah ki raah mein kharch kar dey, to wo tera ye amal qubul nahin kerega yahan tak key to sari taqdir par eman laye, aur (yaqeen key sath) jaan ley ke jo musibat tujhey pahunchi hai wo tujh sey talney wali na thi aur jo musibat tujhey nahin pahunchi, wo tujhey pahunchney wali na thi. aur (jaan ley ke) agar teri maut us aqidey key siwa kisi aur aqidey par hui to to jahannam mein dakhil hoga ."
78,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey huye they, aap key haath main eik lakdi thi, aap uskey sath zamin mein lakeerein laganey lagey ( jaisey koi shakhs gehri soch mein ho to karta hai) , phir aap ney sar uthaya aur farmaya : tum mein sey har shakhs ka thikana jannat ya jahannam mein likh diya gaya hai. arz kya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! phir hum ( likhey huye par) bharosa na kar lein ? farmaya : nahin, amal karo) likhey huye par) bharosa na karo, har kisi key liye wo kaam aasan ho jata hai jis key liye wo paida kya gaya . phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayaat tilawat farmaain ( فَاَمَّا مَنْ اَعْطٰى وَاتَّقٰى » O وَصَدَّقَ بِالْحُسْنٰى O فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْيُسْرٰى O وَاَمَّا مَنْۢ بَخِلَ وَاسْتَغْنٰى O وَكَذَّبَ بِالْحُسْنٰى O فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْعُسْرٰى O )' jisney ( Allah ki raah mein) diya aur (apney rab sey) dara. aur achi baat ki tasdeeq ki to hum bhi usey aasan raastey ki sahulat dengey, lekin jisney bukhl kya aur be-parwai ki aur achi baat ki takzeeb ki to hum bhi us ko tangi aur mushkil key asbab muyassar kar dengey."
79,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : taqatwar momin kamzor momin sey behtar aur Allah ko ziyada pyara hai. aur har eik mein khair mojud hai, jo chiz tujhey faeyda deti hai is mein raghbat kar aur Allah sey madad mang . aajiz na ban. agar tujhey koi musibat aa jaey to yun na keh : agar main is tarah karta, to yun na hota. balke yun keh : Allah ney yehi muqaddar kya tha aur Allah ney jo chaha kya. 'kyonkey (lafz lau ), 'agar' sey shetan ka kaam shuru ho jata hai."
80,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hazrat Adam aur Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ki aapas mein behes ho gaee . Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : aey Adam ! aap hamarey walid hain, aap ney hamen mahroomi ka shikar kar diya aur gunah ka irtikab kar key hamen jannat sey niklwa diya . Adam (Alaihissalam) ney unhen farmaya : aey Musa! Allah ney aap ko sharfe-hum-kalami key liye muntakhab farmaya aur aap ko apney haath sey likh kar Torat di, kya aap mujhey is baat par malamat kartey hain jo Allah ney mujhey paida karney sey chaalis saal pehley meri qismat mein likh di thi? chunanche behes mein Adam (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aa gaey. Adam (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aagey . Adam (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aagey. (teen martaba aap ney farmaya.)"
81,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi banda momin nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke wo chaar chizon par eman rakhey : Allah par jo akela hai uska koi shareek nahin, is baat par ke main (Muhammad) Allah ka Rasool hon, maut key baad zinda ho kar uthney par aur taqdir par ."
82,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik Ansari ladkey ki namaz janaza ada karney key liye bulaya gaya. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! us (bachey) ko Mubarak ho, wo to jannat ki eik chidiya hai, usney na koi gunah kya aur na gunah ki umr ko pahuncha . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Aaisha! ye baat nahin, Allah Taala ney jannat key liye kuch afrad paida kiye hain, unhen uskey liye paida kya jabke wo abhi apney baapon ki pushton mein they aur jahannam key liye kuch afrad paida kiye hain, unhen uskey liye paida kya hai jabke wo abhi apney baapon ki pushton mein they.'"
83,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Quraish key mushrik taqdir key masley mein behes karney key liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye , to ye aayat nazil ho gaee : ( يَوْمَ يُسْحَبُوْنَ فِي النَّارِ عَلٰي وُجُوْهِهِمْ padhi. ذُوْقُوْا مَسَّ سَقَرَ اِنَّا كُلَّ شَيْءٍ خَلَقْنٰهُ بِقَدَر ٍ) jis din unhen chehron key bal aag mein ghasita jaeyga (aur un sey kaha jaeyga : ) tum dozakh ki aag lagney ka maza chakho . beshak hamney har chiz eik andazey key mutabiq paida ki hai."
84,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Muleka (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur un sey taqdir key barey mein kuch kaha , to ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs taqdir key barey mein guftgu kerega, us sey qiyamat key din uskey barey mein sawal hoga aur jo shakhs us mauzoo par kalam nahin kerega, us sey qiyamat key din uskey barey mein sawal nahin kya jaeyga. abul-Hasan al-Qattan ney kaha : hamen Khazim bin Yahya ney , unhen abdul-Malik bin Sanan ney unhen Yahya bin Usman ney usi ( Malik bin Ismail) ki misl riwayat bayan ki."
85,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik roz Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar Sahaba key paas tashrif laye to wo taqdir key barey mein behes kar rahey they. aap ka Chehra Mubarak ghussay sey is qadr surkh ho gaya, goya is par anaar key daney nichod diye gaey hain. (tab) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tumhen is baat ka hukm diya gaya hai? ya kya tumhen us kaam key liye paida kya gaya hai? tum Quran ki aayaat ko eik dusri sey takra rahey ho. tum sey pehli ummaten usi wajeh sey tabah huin thin . Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi majlis sey ghair hazir rehney par khushi nahin hui jis tarah us majlis mein mojud na honey par khushi hui ."
86,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bimari eik sey doosrey ko nahin lagti , badshigooni ki koi haqiqat nahin, na ullu koi chiz hai. 'eik Erabi (dehati) uth kar aap key qarib aaya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! dekhiye na, eik oont ko khaarish ki bimari hoti hai, wo tamam oonton ko khaarish mein mubtala kar deta hai. to aap ney farmaya : ye taqdir hai, pehley oont ko khaarish kis sey lagi?"
87,"Janab Shaaby (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : jab Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) koofa tashrif laye to koofa key chand fuqaha key sath hum bhi khidmat mein hazir huye, hamney un sey arz kya : aap ney jo kuch Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, hamen bhi sunaaiye . unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Adi bin Hatim ! Islam qubul kar ley, salaamat rahega. mainey kaha : Islam kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to gawahi dey ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur main (Muhammad) Allah ka Rasool hun aur to har qism ki, achi buri , shirin o talkh taqdir par eman laye ."
88,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dil ki misal eik par ki si hai, jisey hawaeyn chatiyal maidan mein ultati-paltati rehti hain.'"
89,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Ansari Sahabi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri eik londi hai, kya main us sey azl kar sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : jo uski qismat mein hai wo usey mil hi jaeyga. baad mein wo Sahabi dobara hazir huwa aur kaha : londi ummid sey ho gaee hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo kuch kisi ki qismat mein hota hai, wo ho key rehta hai."
90,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sirf neki hi umr mein izaafey ka baais hoti hai aur taqdir ko mehaz dua hi taalti hai, bila shubha insan ko baaz oqaat eik gunah key irtikab ki wajeh sey rizq sey mehrum kar diya jata hai.'"
91,"Hazrat Suraqa bin Joshum (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya amal un mamlon mein shamil hai jinhen likh kar qalam khushk ho gaya aur uskey barey mein taqdir ka faisla ho chuka ya uska talluq aainda (faisla honey waley maamlat (sey hai? aap ney farmaya : balke wo un umoor mein shamil hai jin ko likh kar qalam khushk ho gaya aur uska andaza ho chuka aur har eik key liye wo kaam aasan ho jata hai jiskey liye wo paida kya gaya ."
92,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is ummat key majusi wo hain jo Allah ki taqdir ka inkar kartey hain, agar wo bimar ho jaeyn, to unki iyaadat na karo, agar mar jaeyn to unkey janaazey mein na jao, aur agar un sey mulaqat ho, to unhen salam na kaho."
93,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main har dost ki dosti sey mustaghni hun. agar main kisi (insan) ko khaleel banata to abu-Bakar ko banata, lekin tumhara sathi Allah ka khaleel hai. hadees key Raavi Wakee (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sathi sey khud ko murad liya hai."
94,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey kabhi kisi maal sey is qadr faeyda hasil nahin huwa, jis qadr abu-Bakar key maal sey mujhey faeyda hasil huwa hai. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) (ye sun kar) aabdeeda ho gaey aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! main bhi aur mera maal bhi aap hi key liye to hai."
95,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : abu-Bakar aur umr tamam pehley pichley adhed umr jannatiyon key sardar hain, nabiyon aur Rasulon key ilawa. aey Ali! jab tak wo dono zinda hain, unhen ye baat na batana ."
96,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( jannat mein) unchey darjey walon ko un sey kam tar darjaat waley is tarah dekhengey jaisey aasman key kisi ufaq mein tulu honey wala sitaara dekha jata hai. bilashuba abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhuma) un ( buland darjaat walon) mein sey hain, balke un sey bhi achey hain."
97,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main nahin janta ke main kitna arsa tumharey andar mojud rahunga , lihaza merey baad (khalifa banney waley) do afrad ki perwi karna . ye farmatey huye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ki taraf ishara kya."
98,"Hazrat ibne-Abu-Muleka sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey suna ke jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki maiyat ko chaar pai par litaya gaya to janaza uthaney sey pehley log ird-gird jama ho kar unkey liye duayen karney lagey . ya farmaya : janaza uthaney sey pehley un ki tareef karney lagey aur unkey liye duayen karney lagey . main bhi un mein shamil tha. main (apney khayalat sey) us waqt chaunka, jab mujhey eik shakhs ka dhakka laga, aur usney merey kandhey par haath rakh diya . mainey mud kar dekha to wo Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) they. unhoney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key liye duaaey rehmat farmaai. phir boley : aap sey badh kar koi shakhs aisa nahin tha jis key amalon jaisey aamal ley kar main Allah key paas janey ki khahish rakhta hun . Allah ki qism ! mujhey yaqin hai ke Allah Taala aap ko aap key dono sathiyon ( Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu)) key sath rakhega . kyonkey main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey aksar is qism key alfaz suna karta tha, aap farmatey they : main aur abu-Bakar aur Umar, (falan jagah) gaey, main aur abu-Bakar o umr dakhil huye, main aur abu-Bakar aur umr bahar nikley. isliye mujhey (pehley hi) yaqin hai ke Allah Taala aap ko zarur aap key dono sathiyon sey mila dega ."
99,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key darmiyan ( chaltey huye ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye . aur farmaya : hamen is tarah ( qabron sey) uthaya jaeyga.
100,"Hazrat abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhuma) pehley aur pichley umr-daraz jannatiyon key sardar hain, lekin nabiyon aur Rasulon key siwa."
101,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke kisi ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sa shakhs aap ko sab sey ziyada pyara hai? aap ney farmaya : Aaisha. arz kiya gaya mardon mein sey kon? farmaya : unkey walid (abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)).
102,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqeeq (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey arz kiya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney kis Sahaba sey sab sey ziyada mohabbat thi? unhoney kaha : abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey. mainey kaha : unkey baad kon (ziyada mehbub they)?  farmaya : umr (Raziallahu anhu). mainey kaha : phir kon? farmaya : abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu)."
103,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Islam laye to Jibril (Alaihissalam) nazil huye aur farmaya : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! umr key Islam laney sey aasman waley (farishtey) bhi khush ho gaey hain.
104,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haq taala sab sey pehley jis shakhs sey musaafa kerega aur sab sey pehley jisey salam kaheyga aur jisey sab sey pehley haath pakad kar jannat mein dakhil kerega, wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) hain."
105,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! Islam ko khas tor par umr bin Khattab key zariey sey quwat bakhsh.
106,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna , wo farma rahey they : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baad sab sey afzal insan abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key baad sab sey afzal insan umr (Raziallahu anhu) hain."
107,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey huye they ke aap ney farmaya : main so raha tha, mainey (khuwab mein) apney aap ko jannat mein dekha , (wahan) mujhey eik mehal key paas eik aurat wuzu karti nazar aai. mainey kaha : ye mehal kis ka hai? usney kaha : umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka hai. mujhey un ki ghairat yad aa gaee, isliye mein (mehal key andar janey key bajaey) wapis aa gaya. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) (ye sun kar) ro padey aur boley : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban ! main aap sey ghairat kar sakta hun."
108,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : Allah Taala ney umr ki zaban par haq rakh diya hai, wo usi key mutabiq baat kartey hain."
109,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har Nabi ka jannat main eik sathi hota hai aur wahan mera sathi Usman bin Affaan hai.
110,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid key darwazey key paas Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey miley aur farmaya : Usman ! ye Jibril (Alaihissalam) hai, unhoney mujhey bataya hai ke Allah Taala ney aap ka nikah Umme Kulsoom (Raziallahu anha) sey Ruqaiyya‬ (Raziallahu anha) key mehar key barabar mehar par kar diya hai, is shart par ke in sey bhi isi tarah husne-suluk karo jis tarah Ruqaiyya‬ (Raziallahu anha) sey kartey they."
111,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik fitney ka zikr kiya aur bataya ke wo bahut qarib hai. (isi beech mein) eik sahab guzrey jinhoney sar par chadar li hui thi, to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is (fitney key) din ye shakhs hidayat par hoga. main jaldi sey utha, Usman Raziallahu anhu key dono bazu pakad kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mutawajjeh huwa aur kaha : kya ye shakhs? aap ney farmaya : (haan)  yehi shakhs."
112,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat ki, unhoney kaha ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Usman ! agar Allah Taala kisi din tujhey khilaafat ki zimme-daari bakhshey, phir munafiq tujh sey wo qamis utarwana chahen jo Allah ney tujhey pahnaai ho, to usey mat utaarna. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen baar yehi baat farmaai. Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey kaha : aap ney logon ko ye hadees kyon nahin sunai thi? unhoney kaha : main isey bhula di gaee thi."
113,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni (aakhiri) bimari key doran mein farmaya : mera ji chahta hai ke merey paas mera eik Sahabi ho.  hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bhejein? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. hamney kaha : umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula lein? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh rahey. hamney kaha : Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula lein? farmaya : haan, Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) hazir ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey tanhai mein guftgu farmaai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey jatey they aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key chehrey key tassurat tabdeel hotey jatey they. Hazrat Qais (Rahimahullah) ka bayan hai ke unhen Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Abu-Sahla (Rahimahullah) ney bataya ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney muhaasra key dinon (din) mein farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey eik wada liya hai aur main is par qaaim hun. Hazrat Ali (bin Muhammad)  ney apni hadees mein kaha : main sabr kartey huye is par qaaim hun. Hazrat Qais (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : sab logon (Sahaba aur Tabe-een)  ka khayal hai ke is hadees mein muhaasre waley din ki taraf ishara tha."
114,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi ummi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey takeed key sath khabar di ke mujh sey sirf momin hi mohabbat rakhega , aur mujh sey sirf munafiq hi nafrat kerega ."
115,Hazrat Saad bin Abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : kya to is baat par razi nahin ke merey sath teri wo nisbat ho jo Harun (Alaihissalam) ki Musa (Alaihissalam) sey thi?
116,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jo Haj ada farmaya, us sey wapsi par safar mein hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. aap ney raastey main eik maqam par padaaw dala aur namaz mein sabko jama honey ka hukm diya. (namaz key baad) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka haath pakad kar farmaya : kya mominon par mera khud unki janon sey ziyada haq nahin? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin. phir farmaya : kya har momin par mera khud uski zaat sey ziyada haq nahin? Sahaba ney kaha : yaqinan hai. to aap ney farmaya : jis ka main dost hun, ye bhi uska dost hai. aey Allah! jo us (Ali) sey dosti rakhey to usi sey dosti rakh. aey Allah! jo us sey dushmani rakhey, to us sey dushmani rakh."
117,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Leila sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat abu-Leila (Raziallahu anhu) raat ko Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key sath guftgu mein shareek hotey they. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sardiyon mein garmiyon ka libas aur garmiyon mein sardiyon ka libas pehan liya kartey they. hamney (abu-Leila (Raziallahu anhu) sey) kaha, aap un (Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) sey uskey mutalliq daryaft karen. (unhoney daryaft kiya to) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : (jang) khaibar key roz Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey bula bheja , jabke meri aankhen dukhti thin. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey aashoob chashm (aankh dukhne ki bimaari) hai. aap ney meri aakhon mein lu'aabe dahan lagaya , aur farmaya : aey Allah ! is sey garmi aur sardi door kar dey. us din key baad sey mujhey garmi ya sardi mehsus nahin hui. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main zarur eik aisa aadmi bhejunga jo Allah sey aur uskey Rasool sey mohabbat rakhta hai aur us sey Allah aur uskey Rasool ko mohabbat hai, wo bhagney wala nahin. log gardanen utha utha kar dekhney lagey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja aur unhen jhandaa ata farmaya."
118,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) jannati jawaanon key sardar hain, aur unkey walid un sey afzal hain."
119,"Hazrat Hubshi bin junaada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : Ali mujh sey hai aur main us sey hun, meri taraf sey sirf Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hi ada kerengey ."
120,"Hazrat Ibaad bin Abdullah (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali Raziallahu anhu ney farmaya : main Allah ka banda hun aur uskey Rasool ka bhai hun, main sabse badh kar sachcha hun, merey baad ye baat wohi kaheyga jo intehai jhoota hai. mainey dusron sey saat saal pehley namaz padhi hai."
121,"Hazrat Saad bin Abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik baar Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) Haj key liye tashrif laye to Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) unkey paas ( mulaqat key liye) gaey. (asnaaey guftgu mein) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka tazkira chhid gaya . Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney unkey mutalliq kuch tanqidi alfaz kahey . Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghussa aa gaya aur farmaya : aap aisey shakhs key barey mein ye baat keh rahey hain jis key mutalliq mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : jis ka maula main hun, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi uska maula (dost) hai.' aur mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna ke aap ney (Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey) farmaya : tera mujh sey wohi talluq hai jo Harun (Alaihissalam) ka Musa (Alaihissalam) sey tha, albatta merey baad koi Nabi nahin. aur mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye bhi suna : aaj main jhanda us shakhs ko dunga jo Allah sey aur uskey Rasool sey mohabbat rakhta hai. (aur wo jhnda Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko mila.)"
122,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Qureza ki jang key moqey par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dushman ki khabar kon layega ? , 'Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ( dobara ( farmaya : dushman ki khabar kon layega ? Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main . teen baar aisey hi huwa . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har Nabi ka eik hawari hota hai aur mera hawari Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) hai."
123,"Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jange-Uhud key din merey liye apney waliden ko jama ( zikr ) farmaya."
124,"Hazrat Urwa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney mujh sey farmaya : Urwa ! tumharey walid aur nana un logon mein shamil hain, jinhoney zakhmi honey key baad bhi Allah aur uskey Rasool key hukm ki taameel ki, yani abu-Bakar aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) ."
125,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey guzrey to aap ney farmaya : ye shahid hai jo zamin par chal raha hai.
126,Hazrat Muawiya bin abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekh kar farmaya : ye un mein sey hai jinhoney apna wada pura kar diya .
127,"Hazrat Musa bin Talha sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha , hum Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas they. unhoney farmaya : main gawahi deta hun ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai aap farma rahey they : ( Talha (Raziallahu anhu)) un logon mein sey hain jinhoney apna wada pura kar diya ."
128,"Hazrat Qais sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka haath dekha jo shal ho chuka tha, unhoney jange-Uhud mein us sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka difaa kya tha."
129,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key siwa kisi Sahabi key mutalliq Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey maa-baap qurban honey key alfaz nahin suney . sirf unhen aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jange-Uhad key moqey par farmaya tha : Saad! teer chalaao, merey maan-baap tum par qurban ."
130,"Hazrat Saad bin Abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jange- Uhud key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney merey liye apney waliden ka naam liya , yani yun farmaya : aey Saad ! teer chalaao , merey maa baap tum par qurban ."
131,"Hazrat Saad bin Abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main pehla Arbi hun, jisney Allah ki raah mein teer chalaya ."
132,"Hazrat Saad bin Abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jis din mainey Islam qubul kya, us din kisi aur shakhs ney Islam qubul nahin kya. saat din tak main musalmanon ki tadaad ka eik tihai raha hun."
133,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid bin Amr bin Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) das afrad ki eik majlis mein daswen fard ki haisiyat sey tashrif farma they (aap key sath no Sahabi they.) aap ney farmaya : abu-Bakar jannati hain, umr jannati hain, Usman jannati hain, Ali jannati hain, Talha jannati hain, Zuber jannati hain, Saad jannati hain, Abdur-Rehman jannati hain.' un sey puchha gaya : (aap ney aath afrad key naam liye hain) nawein sahab kon hain? farmaya : main ."
134,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : main gawahi deta hun ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : hira (pahad) ! thehar ja , tujh par sirf Nabi , Siddiq aur shaheed hain. Raavi ney un hazarat ko shumar kya (jo pahad par they, aur kaha) : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), abu-Bakar , umr , Usman , Ali , Talha , Zuber , Saad , Abdur-Rehman bin Auf aur Saeed bin Zaid Raziallahu anhum ."
135,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Najran walon sey kaha : main tumharey sath eik diyanat daar aadmi bhejunga, jo kama haqqahu diyanat daar hai.' logon ko justju hui . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja ."
136,Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein farmaya : ye is ummat ka diyanat daar aadmi hai.
137,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar main baghair mashwarey key kisi ko khalifa muqarrar karta to Umme abd key betey (Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ) ko khalifa muqarrar karta ."
138,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke abu-Bakar o umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney unhen khushkhabri di ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Quran ko is tarah tar-o-taza padhna chahta hai jis tarah wo nazil huwa , usey chahiye ke ibn Umme abd ( Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ki qirat key mutabiq padhey ."
139,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara izn (ghar mein aaney key liye) yehi hai ke parda uthao, aur tum meri raazdarana guftgu bhi sun saktey ho, yahan tak ke main mana kar dun ."
140,"Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Quraish key kuchh log baaten kar rahey hotey, hum un sey miltey (un ki majlis mein ja pahunchtey)  to wo baat cheet khatam kar detey. hamney ye baat Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko batai to aap ney farmaya : logon ko kya huwa ke wo baaten kar rahey hotey hain phir jab merey ghar walon mein sey kisi shakhs ko dekhtey hain to baat cheet khatam kar detey hain. Allah ki qism ! kisi aadmi key dil mein eman dakhil nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke wo un sey , Allah key liye aur un sey meri qurbat ka lihaz rakhtey huye, mohabbat rakhey."
141,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney mujhey khaleel banaya hai jis tarah Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko khaleel banaya tha. qiyamat key din jannat mein mera maqam aur Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ka maqam dono aamney-samney hongey aur Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) hum dono key) Allah key do doston key darmiyan eik momin hongey .
142,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) key mutalliq farmaya : aey Allah ! main is sey mohabbat rakhta hun to bhi is sey mohabbat rakh , aur jo is sey mohabbat karey us sey bhi mohabbat kar. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein seeney sey laga liya."
143,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) sey mohabbat ki, usney mujh sey mohabbat ki aur jisney un sey bughz rakha usney mujh sey bughz rakha."
144,"Hazrat Yalaa bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ko khaney ki dawat di gaee thi. wo log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath wahan janey key liye rawana huye, dekha to gali mein Husain (Raziallahu anhu) khel rahey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dusron sey aagey badh kar (Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko pakadney key liye)  haath phela diye. wo idhar-udhar bhagney lagey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen hansaate rahey. aakhir unhen pakad liya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apna eik haath un ki thodi key nichey rakha , aur doosra haath unkey sar key pichhley hissey par rakha aur unhen choom liya. phir farmaya : Husain mujh sey hai aur main Husain sey hun, jo Husain sey mohabbat karey , Allah us sey mohabbat karey aur Husain asbaat mein sey eik sabt hain.  Imam Ibne-Maja (Reh.) ney kaha hamein Ali bin Muhammad ney Wakee sey unhoney Sufiyan sey sabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
145,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali , Fatima , Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhum sey farmaya : jis sey tum suleh karo, meri bhi us sey suleh hai aur jis sey tum jang karo, us sey meri bhi jang hai."
146,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha huwa tha ke Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhuma) ney aaney ki ijazat chahi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey ijazat dey do. us pak kiye huye pak baaz ko khush aamadeed."
147,"Hazrat Hani bin Hani (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye to unhoney farmaya : pak kiye huye pak baaz ko khush aamadeed ! mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap ney farmaya : Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) sar sey peir tak eman sey maamur hai."
148,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) par jab bhi do kaam pesh kiye gaey to unhoney ziyada sahih kaam ka intikhaab kya. ,"
149,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney mujhey chaar hazraat sey mohabbat rakhney ka hukm diya hai, aur mujhey khabar di hai ke wo bhi un sey mohabbat rakhta hai.' arz kya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kon kon hain? farmaya, un mein sey eik Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hain. 'ye baat aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen baar farmaai . phir farmaya : aur abu-Zar, Salman aur miqdaad Raziallahu anhum ."
150,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : sab sey pehley Islam ka izhar karney waley saat Hazrat hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , abu-Bakar , Ammar, un ki walida Sumaiya , Suheb, Bilaal, aur miqdaad Raziallahu anhum. Rasoolullah ko to Allah ney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key chacha Abu-Talib key zariey sey (mushrekin ki aziyaton sey) mehfooz rakha, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi Allah ney un ki qom key zariey sey mehfooz rakha, baqi jo hazraat they unhein mushrikon ney pakad liya, unhen lohey ki zirhen pahna kar dhoop mein dal diya, chunanche un mein sey koi bhi aisa na tha jisney (jaan bachaney key liye, zaban sey) mushrekin key matlab ki baat na keh di ho, siwaye Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) key. unhoney Allah ki raah main apni jaan ki parwa na ki aur unki qom ki nazar mein bhi unki koi qadr na thi (isliye koi unki himayat mein nahin boltaa tha) kafiron ney unhen pakad kar bachon key hawaley kar diya, wo unhen Makka ki ghaatiyon mein liye (ghaseet'tey) phirtey they aur Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they : ahad - ahad ( Allah eik hai, eik hai.)"
151,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey Allah ki raah mein takleefen ayen jab kisi aur ko taklifen nahin di jati thin. aur mujhey Allah ki raah mein khof-zada kya gaya jab kisi aur ko daraya dhamkaaya nahin jata tha. baaz oqaat mujh par teesri raat bhi us haal mein aa jati thi ke merey liye aur Bilal key liye khaney ki koi chiz nahin hoti thi jisey koi zi-rooh kha sakey, magar itni si miqdaar mein ke jisey Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki baghal chupa ley."
152,"Hazrat Salim (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke kisi shayer ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key betey Hazrat Bilal (Rahimahullah) ki tareef kartey huye ye keh diya : Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) key betey Bilal har Bilal sey achey hain. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney kaha : to jhoot kehta hai, nahin, balke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) har Bilal sey achey hain."
153,"Hazrat abu-Leila kandi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat khubab (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye to unhoney farmaya : qarib aa kar betho, us jagah bethney ka haq aap sey ziyada kisi ko nahin, siwaye Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) key. phir Hazrat khubab (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko mushrekin ki taklifon key natijey mein kamar par pad janey waley nishaanaat dikhaney lagey."
154,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat mein , ummat par sab sey ziyada reham karney waley abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain, aur Allah key Deen mein sab sey sakht umr (Raziallahu anhu) hain, sab sey ziyada sachi haya waley Usman (Raziallahu anhu) hain, ziyada behtar faisla karney waley Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hain, Allah ki kitab key ziyada aalim Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) hain, halal o haram ka ziyada ilm rakhney waley Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur ilm meeras key ziyada mahir Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) hain. suno ! har ummat ka eik ameen hota hai aur is ummat key ameen (dayanat daar fard) abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) hain.'"
155,"dusri sanad sey isi hadees mein ye alfaz hain, faraaiz (warison key hisson) ka ziyada ilm rakhney waley Zaid bin Sabit hain.'"
156,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap ney farmaya : Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey badh kar baat mein sacha aadmi na zamin ney uthaya , na aasman ney is par saya kya.'"
157,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik reshmi kapda bator hadiya pesh kya gaya . haazirin usey haath mein ley ley kar dekhney lagey (ke kitna umda hai) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum is par tajjub kartey ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan, aey Allah key Rasool! aap ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai! jannat mein Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) key roomaal us sey behtar hain."
158,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat par Rehman ka arsh bhi jhoom utha ."
159,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab sey mainey Islam qubul kya, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi khidmat mein hazir honey sey mana nahin farmaya aur jab bhi mujhey dekha, merey ru-baru muskuraaey. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey shikayat ki ke main ghodey par jam kar nahin beth sakta, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney merey seeney par haath maar kar farmaya : aey Allah! usey Sabit qadmi nasib farma aur usey hidayat deney wala , hidayat yafta bana dey ."
160,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Jibril (Alaihissalam), ya farmaya : eik farishta Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : tum mein sey jo log jange-badar mein shareek huye, tum log unhen kya maqam detey ho? unhoney kaha : hum unhein apney mein afzal shumar kartey hain. farishtey ney kaha, isi tarah hamari nazar mein wo (farishtey jo jange-badar mein shareek huye doosrey)  farishton mein afzal hain."
161,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey sathiyon ko bura bhala mat kaho , qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum mein sey koi agar uhad pahad key barabar sona bhi (Allah ki raah mein) kharch kar dey, to unkey eik mudd, balke aadhey mudd tak nahin pahunch sakta."
162,"Hazrat Nuser bin Zaaluq (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) farmaya kartey they : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba ko bura na kaho, eik Sahaba ka (Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat mein) ghadi bhar theherna, tum mein sey kisi ki zindagi bhar key amalon sey behtar hai."
163,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo ansaar sey mohabbat kerega, Allah us sey mohabbat kerega, aur jo ansaar sey bughz rakhega , Allah us sey bughz rakhega. Shoba (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey Adi sey puchha ke kya tum ney ye hadees Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey) khud  suni hai? to unhoney kaha mujhey unhoney hi ye hadees bayan ki hai."
164,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ansaar badan sey lage hue libas (ki tarah)  hain aur doosrey log chadar (ki tarah) hain. agar log eik wadi ya ghaati ikhtiyar karen aur ansaar dusri wadi ki taraf chalen , to main ansaar ki wadi mein chalunga. aur agar hijrat na hoti, to main ansaar ka eik fard hota."
165,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ansaar par rehmat farmaey, ansaar key beton par aur ansaar key poton par."
166,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey seeney sey lagaya aur farmaya : aey Allah ! isey hikmat sikha dey aur kitab (Quran Majeed)  ka matlab sikha dey."
167,"Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney khawaarij ka zikr kartey huye farmaya : un main eik aadmi hai jis ka haath adhuraa hai, ya farmaya : naqis hai, ya farmaya : chhota sa hai. agar ye khatra na hota ke tum fakhr karney lagogey to main tumhen bata deta ke unhein qatl karney walon key liye Allah ney Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zabane Mubarak sey kya kuchh (sawab aur inaamaat ka)  wada kiya hai. Hazrat Ubeda (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey arz kiya : kya aap ney ye baaten Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (baraahe raast) suni hain? Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney teen baar farmaya : Kaabe ke Rab ki qism ! haan."
168,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aakhiri zamaney mein kuchh log zahir hongey, kam umr (nojawan),  kam aql , (ba-zahir)  badi achchhi baaten kerengey, Quran padheingey, lekin wo unkey galon sey aagey nahin badheyga . wo Islam sey is tarah nikal jaeyngey, jis tarah teer (nishana ban'ney waley)  shikar sey guzar jata hai. jo shakhs unhen miley, usey chaheye ke unhein qatl karey, jo koi unhein qatl kerega, usey Allah sey unkey qatl karney ka sawab milega."
169,"Hazrat abu-Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha , kya aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey harooriya key barey mein koi irshad suna hai? unhoney farmaya : mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aisi jamaat ka zikr kartey suna hai jo bahut ibadat kerengey (yahan tak ke), ''tum un ki namazon key muqabley main apni namazon ko aur unkey rozon key muqabley mein apney rozon ko maamuli samjho ge.'' (lekin) wo Deen sey aisey nikal jaeyngey jis tarah teer shikar sey aar paar ho jata hai. teer andaz teer ko pakad kar uska phal dekhta hai, usey (shikar honey waley janwer ka)  kuch bhi (phal sey laga huwa) nazar nahin aata, putthey ko dekhta hai, to kuchh nazar nahin aata, teer ki lakdi ko dekhta hai to kuchh nazar nahin aata , phir teer key paron ko dekhta hai to shak hota hai ke (janwer key khoon waghera ka) kuch (asar) nazar aa raha hai ya nahin?"
170,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey baad meri ummat mein kuchh aisey log hongey jo Quran padheingey , wo unkey galon sey aagey nahin badheyga , wo Deen sey is tarah nikal jaeyngey jis tarah teer nishana ban'ney waley janwer mein sey guzar jata hai, phir wo (deen mein) wapis nahin ayengey. wo tamam makhluqat mein sey bad-tareen afrad hongey. Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid Abdullah bin Samit Rahimahullah ney farmaya : mainey Hakam bin Amr Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) key bhai Raafey bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey is hadees ka zikr kiya to unhoney farmaya : mainey bhi ye hadees Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai."
171,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key kuchh log Quran padheingey. (iskey bawajood)  wo Islam sey is tarah nikal jaeyngey jis tarah nishana ban'ney waley janwer mein sey teer aar paar ho jata hai."
172,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jaarana maqam par maale ghanimat aur sona taqseem kar rahey they jo Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki jholi mein tha. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) insaf kijiye, aap ney insaf nahin kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : afsos hai tujh par ! agar main insaf nahin karunga to phir merey baad aur kon insaf kerega?  Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! ijazat dijiye ke main us munafiq ki gardan uda dun. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye shakhs bhi apney un sathiyon mein shamil hai jo Quran padheingey , lekin wo unkey galey sey aagey nahin guzreyga, wo Deen sey is tarah nikal jaeyngey jis tarah teer nishana ban'ney waley janwer mein sey paar ho jata hai."
173,"Hazrat ibne Abu Ufee (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khaariji jahannam key kuttey hain."
174,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik jamaat paida hogi jo Quran padheingey , wo unkey halaq sey aagey nahin guzreyga, jab bhi (un mein sey) koi giroh zahir hoga, kaat diya jaeyga.  Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye baat : jab koi giroh zahir hoga, kaat diya jaeyga. bees sey ziyada dafa suni hai. aur farmaya : yahan tak key un mein sey dajjaal zahir hoga."
175,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aakhir zamaney mein , ya farmaya : is ummat mein kuchh log zahir hongey jo Quran padheingey aur wo unkey halqon sey aagey nahin guzreyga, un ki alamat sar mundaanaa hai, jab tum unhein dekho, ya farmaya : jab tum un sey milo, to unhein qatl karo."
176,"Hazrat Abu Ghalib (Reh.) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ye log (khaariji)  aasman key nichey qatl honey waley bad-tareen afrad hain aur jinhein ye log qatl kar den wo behtareen maqtool (shaheed) hain. ye jahannamiyon key kuttey hain, ye musalman they, phir kafir ho gaey. mainey kaha : abu-Umama ! kya ye aap ki (apni) raey hai? unhoney kaha : balke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye baat suni hai."
177,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they, aap ney chaudahwin raat key chaand ki taraf nazar uthai aur farmaya : tum anqarib apney Rab ko dekhogey jis tarah is chaand ko dekhtey ho, tumhen uskey deedar mein mashaqqat nahin hogi, lihaza agar tum sey ho sakey ke suraj tulu honey sey pehley aur ghurub honey sey pehley wali namazon key barey mein maghloob na ho jao, to zarur aisa karo. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ( وَ سَبِّــحْ بِحَمْدِ رَبِّكَ قَبْلَ طُلُوْعِ الشَّمْسِ وَ قَبْلَ الْغُرُوْبِ )''suraj tulu honey sey pehley aur ghurub honey sey pehley apney Rab ki tareef key sath uski tasbih karen.''"
178,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tumhen chaudahwin raat ko chaand dekhney mein mashaqqat hoti hai. Sahaba ney kaha : ji nahin. farmaya : isi tarah qiyamat key din tumhen apney rab ki ziyaarat mein koi mushkil nahin hogi."
179,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Khudri) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum apney Rab ko dekhengey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tumhen dophare key waqt suraj ko dekhney mein koi dushwaari pesh aati hai jabkey (aasman par) badal bhi na ho?  hamney kaha : ji nahi . farmaya : kya tumhen chaudahwin raat ko chaand dekhney mein dushwaari hoti hai jabke badal bhi na ho?   Sahaba ney kaha : ji nahin. farmaya : tumhen Allah ki ziyaarat mein itni hi dushwaari hogi jitni suraj aur chaand dekhney mein hoti hai."
180,"Hazrat abu-Rizeen (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya qiyamat ko hum Allah ki ziyaarat kerengey? aur uski makhluq mein uski kya nishani hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey abu-Rizeen ! kya tum mein sey har shakhs chaand ko is tarah nahin dekhta goya wo akela hi usey dekh raha hai? mainey arz kiya : ji haan (aisey hi hota hai).  farmaya : Allah ziyada azmat wala hai aur ye (chaand) makhluqat mein uski nishani hai."
181,"Hazrat abu-Rizeen (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamara Rab bandon ki maayoosi par hanstaa hai halanke uski taraf sey halaat ki tabdili qarib hoti hai. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya Rab taala hanstaa hai? farmaya : haan. mainey kaha : hum aisey Rab ki khair sey kabhi mehroom nahin hongey jo hanstaa hai."
182,"Hazrat Abu-Rizeen (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! makhluq ko paida karney sey pehley hamara Rab kahan tha? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo badal mein tha, us (badal)  key nichey bhi hawa na thi, aur uskey ooper bhi hawa na thi, aur na wahan koi aur makhluq thi. uska arsh pani par tha."
183,"Hazrat Safwan bin Muharriz Mazni (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik dafa Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) Baitullah ka tawaf kar rahey they, hum bhi unkey sath they, achcha eik aadmi samney aa gaya, usney kaha : aey ibne-Umar ! aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sargoshi key barey mein kya farmatey suna hai? unhoney farmaya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farmatey they : qiyamat key din bandey ko Rab key qarib kiya jaeyga, yahan tak key Allah Taala is par parda dal dega , aur us sey uskey gunahon ka iqrar karaaeyga. farmaeyga : kya to (falan gunah ko) janta hai? banda kaheyga : ya Rab ! pehchanta hun (mainey ye gunah kya hai). yahan tak key jab iqrar sey uski wo haalat ho jaeygi, jo Allah chahega (jab bandey ko yaqin ho jaeyga ke ab zarur sakht saza milegi)  Allah Taala farmaeyga : mainey duniya mein terey un gunahon par parda dal diya tha aur aaj unhein terey liye maaf karta hun, phir usey nekiyon wali kitab daain haath mein dey di jaeygi, aur kafir ya munafiq ko sab haazirin (ehale mehshar) key samney pukar kar kaha jaeyga : ( هَؤُلَاءِ الَّذِينَ كَذَبُوا عَلَى رَبِّهِمْ , أَلَا لَعْنَةُ اللَّهِ عَلَى الظَّالِمِينَ )''ye wo log hain jinhoney apney Rab par jhoot baandha.'' suno ! zalimon par Allah ki lanat hai.  Khalid (bin Haris) ney farmaya : ( عَلَى رُءُوسِ الْأَشْهَادِ)  ''sab haaziriin key samney''   ye lafz munqata' (kati hui) sanad sey marvi (riwayat hue) hai, baqi puri hadees ki sanad muttasil hai."
184,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ehale jannat apni nematon (sey lutf andoz honey) mein (mashghool) hongey, achcha eik Noor numaya hoga. wo sar uthaeyngey to (dekhengey ke) Rab unkey ooper jalwa afroz hoga. wo farmaeyga : aey jannat walo ! tum par salamti hai. is aayat Mubarak mein yehi mazkur hai : ( سَلامٌ قَوْلًا مِّنْ رَّبٍّ رَّحِيْم ٍ )''meharban Rab ki taraf sey salam kaha jaeyga."" Allah Taala un ki taraf dekhega aur wo uska deedar kerengey, jab tak wo Allah Taala ka deedar kartey rahengey, jannat ki kisi nemat ki taraf tawajjoh nahin dengey yahan tak key Allah Taala pardey mein ho jaeyga aur unkey gharon mein uski taraf sey Noor aur barkat reh jaeygi."
185,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey har shakhs sey Allah Taala kalam farmaeyga , jabke bandey aur Rab key darmiyan koi tarjamaan nahin hoga. banda apni daain taraf nazar kerega, to wohi aamal nazar ayengey jo usney aagey bhejey, phir baain taraf nazar kerega, to wohi aamal nazar ayengey jo usney aagey bhejey, phir samney nazar uthaeyga, to samney (jahannam ki) aag nazar aayegi, lihaza jo shakhs kisi bhi tarah aag sey bach sakta hai, wo zarur apna bachao kerey. agar-che aadhi khajoor key zariey sey hi ho sakey."
186,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Qais Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do jannaten chaandi ki hain, unkey bartan aur un mein mojud sab cheezen chaandi ki hain. aur do jannaten soney ki hain, unkey bartan aur un mein mojud sab kuchh soney ka hai aur logon ko Allah ki ziyaarat sey koi rukawat nahin hogi . siwaye iskey ke Allah key chehrae-aqdas par kibriyaai (badhaai) ki chadar hogi. jannate-adn mein (ye ziyaarat hogi)."
187,"Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ( لِلَّذِينَ أَحْسَنُوا الْحُسْنَى وَزِيَادَةٌ )''jinhon ney neki ki, unkey liye behtareen (jaza) hai aur mazeed (inaam bhi)."" aur farmaya : jab jannati jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyngey aur jahannami jahannam mein pahunch jaeyngey to eik aawaz deney wala aawaz dega : aey jannat walo ! Allah ney tum sey eik wada kar rakha hai ab wo usey pura karna chahta hai, wo kahengey : wo kya hai? (kya abhi aur nemat bhi baqi hai?), kya Allah Taala ney hamari nekiyon key wazan bhari nahin kar diye? aur hamarey chehrey safed nahin kar diye, hamein jannat mein dakhil nahin kar diya aur jahannam sey najat nahin dey di? (ab us sey badh kar kon sey nemat ho sakti hai jo milney wali hai?)  aap ney farmaya : phir Allah Taala parda hata dega, to log Allah Taala ka deedar kerengey. Allah ki qism ! Allah ney unhein koi nemat ata nahin ki hogi jo apni ziyaarat sey ziyada piyari aur us sey ziyada aankhen thandi karney wali ho."
188,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : sab taarifein Allah key liye hain jo tamam aawaazon ko sunta hai. takraar karney wali khatoon Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur main kamrey key eik koney mein thi. wo (Nabi (Alaihissalam) sey) apney khawind ki shikayat kar rahi thi aur mujhey uski baat sunai nahin dey rahi thi. Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai : ( قَدْسَمِعَ اللّٰهُ قَوْلَ الَّتِيْ تُجَادِلُكَ فِيْ زَوْجِهَا )''Allah taala ney us (aurat) ki baat sun li jo aap sey apney khawind key barey mein takraar kar rahi thi.''"
189,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney makhluqat ko paida karney sey pehley apney haath sey apni zaat key barey mein ye tehreer farma diya hai : meri rehmat merey ghazab sey badh gaee.
190,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab jange uhad mein (merey walid)  Abdullah bin Amr bin Haram (Raziallahu anhu) shaheed ho gaey, to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : aey Jabir ! kya main tujhey na bataun ke Allah Taala ney terey walid sey kya farmaya? dusri sanad sey is hadees mein ye lafz hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Jabir ! kya baat hai, mein tujhey dukhi dil dekh raha hun? mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey walid shaheed ho gaey aur bachchey aur qarz chhod gaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main tujhey khushkhabri na dun ke Allah ney terey walid sey kis andaz sey mulaqat ki? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! zarur farmaiye, farmaya : Allah Taala ney jis sey bhi kalam kiya hai, pardey key peechhey sey kiya hai, lekin terey walid sey baghair hijaab key kalam farmaya. aur farmaya merey bandey ! mujh sey kisi tamanna ka izhar kar, main tujhey ata farmaaunga. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ya Rab ! mujhey zinda kar dey, main dobara teri raah mein qatl ho jaun. Allah Taala ney farmaya : mera ye faisla pehley sey ho chuka hai ke unhen duniya mein wapis nahin bheja jaeyga. unhoney kaha : ya Rab ! phir merey pasmandagaan ko pegham pahuncha dey. tab Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di : ( وَلَا تَحْسَبَنَّ الَّذِيْنَ قُتِلُوْا فِيْ سَبِيْلِ اللّٰهِ اَمْوَاتًا padhi. بَلْ اَحْيَاۗءٌ عِنْدَ رَبِّھِمْ يُرْزَقُوْنَ )''jo log Allah ki raah mein qatl kar diye gaey unhein murda na samjho, balke wo zinda hain apney Rab key paas, unhen rizq diya jata hai.''"
191,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala do aadmiyon (key maamley) sey hanstaa hai ke un mein sey eik , doosrey ko qatl karta hai aur wo dono jannat mein dakhil ho jatey hain. (wo is tarah hota hai ke) eik shakhs Allah ki raah mein jang karta hai aur shaheed ho jata hai, phir Allah Taala qatil (ko tauba ki tofiq deta hai aur us)  ki tauba qubul farmata hai. wo Islam qubul kar key Allah ki raah mein jang karta hai aur shaheed ho jata hai (is tarah qatil aur maqtool dono shaheed ho kar jannat hasil kar letey hain).''"
192,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala qiyamat key din zamin ko haath mein ley lega aur aasman ko daain haath sey lapet dega , phir farmaeyga : main badshah hun, zamin key badshah kahan hain?"
193,"Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Bat'haa maqam par eik jamaat mein tha. majlis mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif farma they. eik badli guzri to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uski taraf dekha aur farmaya : tum log isey kya kehtey ho?  unhoney kaha : ''sahaab.'' farmaya : aur badal bhi (kehtey ho). unhoney kaha : aur badal bhi . farmaya : aur abr bhi . unhoney kaha : aur abr bhi . farmaya : tumharey khayal main tum sey aasman ka fasla kis qadr hai?  unhoney kaha : hamein to malum nahin. farmaya : tum sey uska fasla ikhattar (71) ya behttar (72) ya tehattar (73) saal ka hai. us sey ooper aasman (ki motaai) bhi isi qadr hai.  yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney saat aasman (is andaz sey) shumar farmaey. phir farmaya : phir saatwen aasman key ooper eik samandar hai uskey ooper key hissey aur nichey key hissey key darmiyan itna fasla hai jitna eik aasman sey doosrey aasman tak hai. us sey ooper aath mendhey hain (arsh uthaney waley farishtey, jinki surat mendhon ki si hai). unkey khuron aur ghutnon key darmiyan itna fasla hai jitna eik aasman sey doosrey aasman tak hai. phir un ki pushton par arshe Ilaahi hai, uskey ooper key hissey aur nichey key hissey key darmiyan itna fasla hai jitna eik aasman sey doosrey aasman tak hai. phir Allah us sey bhi ooper hai, wo barkaton wala aur bulandiyon wala hai."
194,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Allah Taala aasman mein kisi kaam ka faisla farmata hai, to farishtey farmane Ilaahi sun kar apney par hila kar khushu ka izhar kartey hain. (wo aawaz itni pur haibat hoti hai) goya wo humwaar patthar par zanjeer (key takraaney ki aawaz) hai. yahan tak key jab unkey dilon sey khof ka asar khatam hota hai to (eik doosrey sey) kehtey hain : tumharey Rab ney kya farmaya? wo kehtey hain : sach farmaya , aur wo bulandiyon wala, kibriyaai wala hai. phir chori chupey sun'ney waley usey sun'ney ki koshish kartey hain jo eik doosrey key ooper hotey hain. to (un mein sey koi) eik lafz sun leta hai aur apney sey nichey waley ko batata hai. kabhi to usey Shahab Saaqib aa leta hai, is sey pehle ke wo apney sey nichey waley ko bataey, jisey wo jadugar ya kaahin ki zaban par jari karey. aur kabhi us tak nahin pahunchta yahan tak key wo apney sey nichey waley ko bata deta hai. wo uskey sath (apney paas sey) sau jhoot mila deta hai. un mein sey sachchi baat wohi Sabit hoti hai jo aasman sey suni gaee thi."
195,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Ash-ari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamarey darmiyan khadey ho kar (khutba diya, us mein) paanch baaten irshad farmaeen. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala sota nahin, na sona uski shaan key laaiq hai, wo meezaan taraazu ko jhukaataa aur buland karta hai, uski taraf din key amalon sey pehley raat key amal, aur raat key amalon sey pehley din key amal buland kiye jatey hain, uska parda Noor hai, agar wo usey hata dey, to uskey Chehrey Mubarak key jalwe sey uski wo tamam makhluq jal jaey jis tak uski nazar pahunchti hai."
196,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala sota nahin, na sona uski shaan key laaiq hai. wo meezaan (tarazu) ko jhukaataa aur buland karta hai. uska parda Noor hai agar wo usey hata dey to uskey Chehrey Mubarak ka jalwa har us chiz ko jala dey jis par uski nazar padey. iskey baad (Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid) Hazrat abu-Ubaida (Rahimahullah) ney ye aayat tilawat ki : ( أَنْ بُورِكَ مَنْ فِي النَّارِ وَمَنْ حَوْلَهَا وَسُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ )''ba-barkat hai wo jo is aag mein hai, aur barkat diya gaya hai wo jo uskey Aas paas hai aur paak hai Allah, jo tamam jahano ka paalne-wala hai.''"
197,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ka daayan haath bharpur hai, koi shai us (key khazanon) ko kam nahin karti, wo raat din kasrat se Ata farmata hai. uskey doosrey haath mein meezaan (tarazu) hai, wo tarazu ko ooncha karta hai aur jhukaataa hai. ghor karo jab sey Allah ney aasman ko aur zamin ko paida kya hai, (tab sey ab tak (kis qadr) be-hisab kharch kar diya hoga? iskey bawajud jo kuch uskey haathon mein hai is mein koi kami nahin hui."
198,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , jabke aap member par tashrif farma they, aap farma rahey they : jabbaar apney aasmano ko aur apni zamin ko apney haath mein ley ley ga. ye farmatey huye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni mutthi band ki, phir usey kholney aur band karney lagey. (farmaya :) phir farmaeyga : jabbaar to main hun, (duniya key naam nihad) jabbaar (aaj) kahan hain? mutakabbir kahan hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ney ye alfaz is qadr josh sey irshad farmaai ke) daain baain jhukney lagey yahan tak ke mainey member ki taraf nazar ki, to wo nichey tak itna hil raha tha ke main (dil mein) keh raha tha kahin wo (member)  Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gira to na dega?"
199,"Hazrat nawaas bin Samaan Kilaabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : har dil Rahmaan ki ungliyon mein sey do ungliyon key darmiyan hai, wo chahey usey sidha (hidayat par qaaim) rakhey, chahey to tedha (aur gumrah) kar dey. aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : (یَا مُثَبِّتَ الْقُلُوْبِ ثَبِّتْ قُلُوْبَنَا عَلٰی دِیْنِک) ''aey dilon ko Sabit rakhney waley ! hamarey dilon ko apney Deen par qaaim rakh.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meezaan Rahmaan key haath mein hai, wo qiyamat tak kuchh logon ko buland karta rahega aur kuchh logon ko past karta rahega."
200,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala teen afrad ko dekh kar hanstaa hai (aur khush hota hai) namaaziyon ki saf, aur jo shakhs raat key oqaat mein namaz padhta hai, aur jo shakhs (fauj key) dastey key peechey (sathiyon ka difaa kartey huye) jang karta hai.'"
201,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Haj key dinon mein logon sey mulaqatein kartey they aur farmatey they : kya koi aadmi hai jo mujhey apni qom mein ley jaey? Quraish to mujhey apney rab key kalam ki tableegh sey roktey hain.'"
202,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke aayat mubaraka : ( كُلَّ يَوْمٍ هُوَ فِيْ شَاْنٍ ) har roz wo eik shaan mein hai. ki wazahat kartey huye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye bhi uski shaan hai ke wo gunah maaf karta hai, pareshani door karta hai, kisi qom ko bulandiyon sey nawazta hai aur kisi ko past kar deta hai.'"
203,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney achcha tariqa jari kya aur is par amal kya gaya, usey uska sawab milega aur un logon key sawab key barabar (mazeed sawab) milega, jo is par amal kerengey. un (baad walon) key sawab mein koi kami nahin hogi. aur jis shakhs ney bura tariqa ejaad kya, phir is par amal kya gaya, usey uska gunah hoga aur un logon key gunah key barabar (mazeed gunah) hoga, jo is par amal kerengey, un (baad walon) key gunah mein bhi koi kami nahin hogi."
204,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (haazirin ko) uski madad ki targheeb dilai. (haazirin mein sey) eik aadmi ney kaha : merey paas itna maal hai (main usey bator sadqa deta hun) chunanche majlis mein sey har shakhs ney usey (hasbe-istataat) kam ya ziyada sadqa diya, koi bhi sadqa diye baghair na raha. tab Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney achcha tariqa jari kya, phir us (tariqey) par amal kya gaya, usey uska pura sawab milega, aur un logon (key barabar amal) ka sawab bhi, jinhoney uski perwi ki, aur unkey sawab mein koi kami nahin hogi aur jisney bura tariqa (gunah ka kaam) shuru kya, phir us (tariqey) par amal kya gaya, usey uska pura gunah hoga. aur un logon (key barabar amal) ka gunah bhi, jinhoney uski perwi ki, albatta unkey gunah mein koi kami nahin hogi."
205,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bulaney wala kisi gumrahi ki taraf bulaey, phir uski perwi ki jaey to usey un logon key gunah key barabar (gunah) hoga, jinhoney uski perwi ki, aur unkey apney gunah mein bhi kami nahin hogi. aur jis bulaney waley ney hidayat ki taraf bulaya, phir uski perwi ki gaee to usey bhi perwi karney walon key barabar sawab milega, aur unkey sawab mein bhi kami nahin hogi."
206,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hidayat ki taraf bulaya , usey perwi karney walon key sawab key barabar sawab milega , us sey unkey ajr o sawab mein kami nahin aayegi, aur jisney gumrahi ki taraf bulaya, usey perwi karney walon key gunahon key barabar gunah hoga, us sey unkey gunahon mein kami nahin aayegi ."
207,"Hazrat abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney achchha tariqa jari kya, is par us (ki wafat) key baad amal hota raha , usey uska apna sawab bhi milega aur un logon key barabar (mazeed) sawab bhi milega, albatta unkey ajr aur sawab mein koi kami nahin ki jaeygi, aur jisney bura riwaaj nikala , phir uskey (marney key) baad is par amal hota raha , usey uska apna gunah bhi hoga aur un logon key gunah key barabar (mazeed) gunah bhi hoga, albatta unkey gunahon mein koi kami nahin ki jaeygi."
208,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo dawat deney wala kisi (achchhi ya buri) chiz ki taraf dawat deta hai, wo qiyamat key din is tarah khada kiya jaeyga ke wo apni dawat key amal sey juda nahin ho sakeyga, jis chiz ki taraf bhi usney dawat di ho agar-che kisi aadmi ney eik hi aadmi ko dawat di ho."
209,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney meri kisi sunnat ko zinda kiya, phir is par logon ney amal kiya, usey us sunnat par amal karney walon key barabar sawab milega, aur unkey sawab mein koi kami nahin hogi. aur jisney koi bidat ejaad ki, phir is par amal kiya gaya, usey amal karney walon key barabar gunah hoga, aur amal karney walon key gunah mein bhi koi kami nahi hogi."
210,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : jisney meri kisi aisi sunnat ko zinda kiya jo merey baad murda ho gaee thi, usey un logon key sawab key barabar sawab milega jo is par amal kerengey, us sey (perwi karney waley) logon key sawab mein bilkul kami nahin aayegi. aur jisney koi bidat ejaad ki jo Allah aur uskey Rasool ko pasand nahin, usey un logon key gunah key barabar gunah hoga jo is par amal kerengey. us sey (perwi karney waley) logon key gunah mein bilkul kami nahin aayegi."
211,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtar wo hai jisney Quran seekha aur sikhaya. eik riwayat mein Raavi Sufiyan key ye lafz hain : tum mein sey afzal wo hai."
212,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey afzal wo hai jo Quran ka ilm hasil karey aur uski taalim dey."
213,Aasim bin Bahadla ney Hazrat Musab bin Saad sey aur unhoney apney walid Hazrat Saad bin Abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey wo log behtar hain jo Quran sikhen aur sikhaaen. Aasim ney kaha : Musab bin Saad ney mujhey haath sey pakad kar us jagah bithaya ke main Quran padhaaun.
214,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo momin Quran padhta hai uski misal turanjabeen ki si hai jis ka zaiqa bhi achcha hai aur bu bhi khushgawar hai. aur wo momin jo Quran nahin padhta , uski misal khushk khajoor ki si hai ke uska zaiqa achcha hai lekin (us mein) khushbu nahin. jo munafiq Quran padhta hai uski misal naazbo ki si hai, uski khushbu to achi hai lekin zaiqa talkh hai, aur jo munafiq Quran nahin padhta, uski misal tummey ki si hai uska zaiqa bhi talkh hai aur khushbu bhi nahin ."
215,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon mein sey kuch afrad Allah waley hotey hain. 'Sahaba kiram ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! wo kon log hain? farmaya : Quran waley, wohi Allah waley aur uskey khas bandey hain.'"
216,"Hazrat Ali bin abu Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Quran padha aur usey hifz kya, Allah Taala usey jannat mein dakhil kerega aur uskey ghar walon mein sey das aisey afrad key haq mein uski shafaat qubul kerega jin par (gunahon ki wajeh sey) jahannam wajib ho chuki hogi."
217,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Quran seekho, phir usey padho aur so raho. (raat ko namaz mein tilawat karo, lekin sari raat namaz na padho balke kuch waqt aaram bhi karo) kyonkey Quran , usey seekhney waley aur uskey sath qiyam karney waley ki misal aisey hai jaisey chamdey ki eik thaili kastoori sey bhari hui ho aur uski khushbu har jagah mehakti ho. aur jisney Quran seekha, phir so raha halanke Quran uskey seeney mein hai uski misal is tarah hai jaisey chamdey ki thaili mein kastoori ho aur uska munh (rassi waghera sey kas kar) baandh diya gaya ho."
218,"Hazrat abu-Tufail Aamir bin Waasila (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Asfan key maqam par Hazrat Nafey bin Abdul Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey mulaqat ki. unhein Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Makka ka governer muqarrar farmaya tha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aap wadiye Makka key bashindon par (un key maamlat ki dekh bhaal key liye) apna naaib kisey muqarrar kar key aaye hain? unhoney kaha : mainey ibne Abzi (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna qaaim maqam muqarrar kiya hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ibne Abzi kon sahab hain? unhoney kaha : hamarey Mola (azad karda ghulam) hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aap ney eik Mola ko un par haakim muqarrar kar diya? unhoney kaha : wo kitabullah key aalim hain, ilm meeras key bhi aalim hain, aur faisla karney ki salahiyat bhi rakhtey hain. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (waqaee sach) farmaya tha : Allah Taala is kitab (key ilm aur is par amal) ki wajeh sey bahut sey logon ko buland maqam ata farmaeyga aur is sey aeraz ki wajeh sey doosrey logon ko past (aur zaleel) kar dega."
219,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey mukhatib kar key farmaya : Abu-Zar ! agar to subah ko (ilm seekhney key liye) nikley aur Allah ki kitab ki eik aayat seekh ley, ye terey liye sau rakat (nafl) namaz padhney sey behtar hai. aur agar to subh nikal kar ilm ka eik baab seekh ley, chahey is par amal kar sakey ya na kar sakey, ye terey liye hazar rakat (nafl) namaz padhney sey behtar hai."
220,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala jis key sath bhalai ka irada farmata hai, usey Deen ki samajh ata kar deta hai."
221,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : neki aadat hai aur gunah eik jhagda hai. aur Allah Taala jis key liye bhalai ka irada farmata hai, usey Deen ki samajh ata kar deta hai."
222,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik faqeeh (deen ki sahih samajh rakhney wala aalim) shetan ko eik hazar (jahil) ibadat guzar afrad sey ziyada nagawar aur bhari hota hai."
223,"Hazrat Kasir bin Qais (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main dimashq ki Jaamey masjid mein Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke aap key paas eik aadmi aa gaya, usney kaha : Abu-Darda ! main Madina sey aaya hun. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key shehar sey. kyonkey mujhey malum huwa hai ke aap eik hadees Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey hain aur main chahta hun ke aap ki zabani wo hadees sunoon. Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aap tijarat key silsiley main to nahin aaye? usney kaha : ji nahin farmaya : kisi aur kaam sey bhi nahin aaye? usney kaha : ji nahin. farmaya : agar ye baat hai to eik khush khabri sun lo: mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs ilm ki talash mein kisi raah par chalta hai, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat ki raah aasan farma deta hai aur farishtey ilm key mutalaashi sey khush ho kar uskey liye apney par jhuka detey hain aur ilm key talabgar key liye aasman aur zamin ki har makhluq duaaey maghfirat karti hai yahan tak key pani mein machliyan bhi uskey liye duayen karti hain aur aalim ko ibadat guzar par aisi fazilat hasil hai jaisi fazilat chaand ko baqi tamam sitaron par hasil hai. ulama anbiyaae-kiraam key waris hain, nabiyon ney virasat mein Dinar aur dirham nahin chhodey, unhoney to ilm ka tarka chhoda hai, jisney usey hasil kiya, usney nabiyon ki virasat mein sey wafir (ziyada) hissa paa liya."
224,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ilm talab karna har musalman par farz hai. aur ilm ko na-ehalon key samney rakhney wala aisa hai jaisey khinzeeron ko jawaharat, motiyon aur soney key haar pahnaaney wala."
225,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kisi musalman ki eik duniyaawi pareshani door ki, Allah Taala uski qiyamat ki pareshaniyon mein sey eik pareshani door kerega, aur jisney musalman ka parda rakha, Allah Taala duniya aur aakhirat mein uska parda rakhega. aur jisney kisi mushkil mein mubtala shakhs par aasani ki, Allah Taala duniya aur aakhirat mein is par aasani farmaeyga, aur Allah Taala apney bandey ki madad karta rehta hai jab tak banda apney bhai ki madad mein mashghool rehta hai, aur jo shakhs ilm ki talash mein raasta tey karta hai, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat ka raasta aasan kar deta hai, aur jab bhi kuchh log Allah key kisi ghar mein jama ho kar Allah ki kitab ki tilawat kartey aur usey baham (aapas mein) seekhtey sikhatey hain, to farishtey unkey gird halqa kar letey hain, un par sakeenat nazil hoti hai, un par rehmat saya figan ho jati hai, aur Allah Taala apney paas waley (muqarrab farishton) mein unka zikr farmata hai. aur jis ka amal usey peechhey kar dey, uska nasab usey aagey nahin badha sakta."
226,"Hazrat zar bin Habish (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya ke main Hazrat Safwan bin Asaal muraadi (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. unhoney kaha : kis kaam sey aaye ho? mainey kaha : ilm (hasil kar key logon mein) phelaney key liye. unhoney kaha : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghar sey ilm ki talash mein nikalta hai uskey amal sey khush ho kar farishtey uskey liye par jhukaatey hain."
227,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye irshad farmatey suna hai : jo shakhs meri is masjid mein aaye, aur uska irada sirf koi achchhi baat seekhnaa ya sikhana ho (koi dunyawi gharz na ho) to uska darja Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ka sa hai. aur jo shakhs kisi aur maqsad key liye (masjid mein) aaya. wo us aadmi ki tarah hai jiski nazar kisi aur key maal par ho."
228,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is ilm (ilm deen) ko uskey qabz honey sey pehley pehley hasil kar lo. qabz honey ka matlab ye hai ke usey utha liya jaeyga. iskey baad aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney darmiyani ungli aur angoothey key sath wali ungli mila kar ishara kiya aur farmaya : aalim aur Talibe ilm sawab mein shareek hain aur doosrey logon mein koi khair nahin."
229,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney eik hujre Mubarak sey bahar nikley aur masjid mein tashrif ley gaey. dekha ke wahan do halqey hain, eik halqey key log Quran Majeed ki tilawat kar rahey they aur Allah sey duayen mang rahey they. doosrey halqey key log ilm seekhney aur sikhaaney mein mashghool they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab log neki mein mashghool hain, ye log Quran ki tilawat kar rahey hain aur Allah sey duayen kar rahey hain, agar Allah Taala chahega to inhen un ki matlooba cheezen dey dega, aur chahega to nahin dega . aur ye log ilm seekh rahey hain aur sikha rahey hain aur mujhey bhi ilm sikhaaney wala bana kar bheja gaya hai. chunanche aap unkey sath beth gaey."
230,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us shakhs ko khush rakhey jisney mera kalam suna, phir usey  dusron tak  pahuncha diya. baaz logon key paas fiq'h ki baat hoti hai, aur wo khud faqeeh nahin hotey . baaz log fiq'h ki baat apney sey ziyada faqeeh aadmi tak pahuncha detey hain.  Ali bin Muhammad ki eik riwayat mein ye izafa hai, 'musalman ka dil teen chizon mein khayanat nahin karta, amal ko khaalis Allah key liye anjam dena, musalmanon key Aaimma ki khair-khahi karna aur musalmanon ki jamaat mein shamil rehna."
231,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Mina mein maqame khaif par khadey ho kar farmaya : Allah Taala us shakhs ko khush rakhey jisney mera kalam suna, phir isey (doosron tak) pahuncha diya. baaz logon key paas fiq'h ki baat hoti hai aur wo faqeeh nahin hotey. baaz log fiq'h ki baat apney sey ziyada faqeeh aadmi tak pahuncha detey hain. Muhammad bin Is-haq key doosrey do shagirdon Yala aur Saeed bin Yahya ney ye riwayat un (Muhammad bin Is-haq) sey bayan ki to Muhammad bin Is-haq aur Imam Zohri key darmiyan wasta bayan nahin kiya."
232,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us shakhs ko khush rakhey , jisney hamari koi baat suni , phir usey ( dusron tak ( pahunchaya , baaz oqaat jisey hadees pahunchaai jati hai, wo ( baraah raast) sunney waley sey ziyada yad rakhney wala hota hai."
233,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbani key din khutba diya aur farmaya : jo shakhs hazir hai, wo ghair mojud tak (meri ye baaten) pahuncha dey . baaz oqaat jis shakhs ko baat pahunchaai jati hai, wo (baraahe-raast) sunney waley sey ziyada yad rakhney wala hota hai.'"
234,"Hazrat Muawiya Qushairi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suno ! jo shakhs mojud hai, wo ghair mojud tak pahuncha dey ."
235,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo log mojud hain, wo unhein pahuncha den jo mojud nahin."
236,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us shakhs ko khush rakhey jisney mera kalam suna, usey yad rakha, phir meri taraf sey (riwayat kartey huye (usey) dusron tak) pahuncha diya . baaz logon key paas fiq'h (aur ilm) ki baat hoti hai aur wo khud faqeeh nahin hotey . baaz log fiqh ki baat apney sey ziyada faqeeh aadmi tak pahuncha detey hain."
237,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kuch log neki ki chabiyan aur burai key taaley hotey hain aur kuch log burai ki chabiyan aur neki key taaley hotey hain. us shakhs ko Mubarak ho jis key haath mein Allah ney neki ki chabiyan dey din aur us shakhs key liye halakat hai jis key haath mein Allah ney burai ki chabiyan dey din ."
238,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : neki key kuch khazaney hain aur un khazanon ki chabiyan hain. Mubarak hai us bandey ko jisey Allah ney neki ki chaabi aur burai ka taala bana diya, aur tabahi hai us bandey key liye jisey Allah ney burai ki chaabi aur neki ka taala bana diya ."
239,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : aalim key liye har wo chiz duaaey maghfirat karti hai jo aasman mein hai aur jo zamin mein hai yahan tak key samandar mein machliyan bhi (uskey haq mein duaaey-maghfirat karti hain.)"
240,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo ( kisi ko) ilm sikhata hai, usey is par amal karney waley key barabar sawab milta hai aur amal karney waley key sawab mein kami nahin hoti ."
241,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insan (marney key baad) apney peechey jo kuch chhod kar jata hai un mein sey behtareen cheezen teen hain : nek aulad jo uskey haq mein dua kerey. sadqa jaariya jiska sawab usey pahunchta rahey, aur wo ilm jis par uskey baad amal hota rahey.) Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid (abul-Hasan al-Qataan ney apney ustad Abu Hatim ki sanad sey abu-Qatada sey yehi riwayat samaa, key seedhey sey bayan ki hai."
242,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ko wafat key baad jo nek amal pahunchtey hain, un mein ye bhi hain : jis ilm ki taalim di aur usey phelaya, nek aulad jo peechey chhodi, Quran Majeed ka nuskha jo kisi ko virasat mein mila, masjid jo usney taamir ki, musafir khana jo usney qaaim kya, nehar jo usney jari ki ya sadqa jo usney apni zindagi mein sehat ki haalat mein nikala, un sab ka sawab uski maut key baad usey milta rehta hai."
243,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey afzal sadqa ye hai ke musalman aadmi kisi chiz ka ilm hasil kerey. phir apney musalman bhai ko uski taalim dey ."
244,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi us haal mein nahin dekha gaya ke aap tek laga kar khana kha rahey hon, na is haal mein dekha gaya ke do aadmi aap key peechey peechey chal rahey hon. (Imam Ibne-Maja rahimahullah key shagrid) abul-Hasan al-Qattan ney apni aali sanad sey yehi hadees Hammad bin Salma key doosrey do shagirdon sey bhi bayan ki hai."
245,Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shadeed garmi mein baqee al-gharqad ki taraf tashrif ley ja rahey they. doosrey hazraat aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key peechey chaley aa rahey they. aap ney unkey jooton ki aawaz suni to nagawari mehsus hui . lihaza aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth gaey yahan tak key Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ko aagey nikal janey diya taake aap key dil mein fakhr ki koi keyfiyat paida na ho jaey .
246,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaltey to Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum aap sey aagey chaltey they aur aap key peechey farishton key liye jagah chhod detey they.
247,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey paas log ilm ki talash mein ayengey . jab tum unhein dekho to kaho : marhaba, khush aamadeed jinkey haq mein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wasiyat ki. aur unhein wo chiz do jo zakhira kiye janey key qabil hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustad Muhammad bin Haris farmatey hain : mainey apney ustaad Hakam bin abda sey puchha : qabile-zakhira chiz deney ka kya matlab hai? unhoney farmaya : uska matlab hai ke unhen ilm sikhaao."
248,"Ismail (bin muslim) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Hazrat Hasan ( Basri) (Rahimahullah) ki iyaadat key liye unkey yahan gaey ( hum logon ki tadaad itni ziyada thi ke) kamra hum logon sey bhar gaya, Hasan ( Basri) (Rahimahullah) ney apney paon samet liye aur farmaya : (eik baar) hum Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki bimar pursi key liye unkey yahan gaey yahan tak key kamra bhar gaya to unhoney bhi paon samet liye they aur farmaya tha : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye yahan tak key kamra bhar gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pehlu key bal letey huye they. hamen dekh kar qadam Mubarak samet liye . phir farmaya : merey baad tumharey paas bahut sey log ilm ki talab mein ayengey, tum unhein khush aamadeed kehna, unhein duayen dena aur unhein taalim dena . Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! hamen to aisey log miley jinhoney hamen na marhaba kaha , na duayen den aur taalim bhi is tarah di ke hum unkey paas jatey they aur wo hum sey be rukhi ka izhar kartey they."
249,"Abu Harun Abdi sey riwayat hai, usney farmaya : hum log jab Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey to wo farmatey : unhen khush aamadeed jinkey barey mein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wasiyat ki hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen farmaya tha : log (deen mein) tumharey tabey hain, wo duniya key ( door daraz) ilaqon sey tumharey paas Deen ki samajh hasil karney key liye ayengey . main wasiyat karta hun ke jab wo tumharey paas ayen to un sey bhalai karna ."
250,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik dua ye bhi thi : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّى أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ عِلْمٍ لاَ يَنْفَعُ وَمِنْ دُعَاءٍ لاَ يُسْمَعُ وَمَنْ قَلْبٍ لاَ يَخْشَعُ وَمِنْ نَفْسٍ لاَ تَشْبَعُ) aey Allah ! main teri panah mein aata hun us ilm sey jo faeyda na dey , us dua sey jo qubul na ho, us dil sey jo ( terey samney) aajizi na karey aur us nafs sey jo sair na ho."
251,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ( اللهم انْفَعْنِى بِمَا عَلَّمْتَنِى وَعَلِّمْنِى ما يَنْفَعُنِى وَزِدْنِى عِلْمًا وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ عَلَى كُلِّ حَالٍ ) aey Allah! to mujhey jo ilm nasib farmaaey us sey mujhey faeyda pahuncha aur mujhey wo ilm dey jo mujhey faeyda dey aur merey ilm mein izafa farma . aur har haal mein Allah ki tareef hai."
252,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo ilm Allah ki raza key liye hasil kya jata hai, jisney usey duniya ka maal o mataa hasil karney key liye seekha, usey qiyamat key din jannat ki khushbu nahin aayegi.) Imam Ibne-Maja Rahimahullah key shagrid (abul-Hasan al-Qattan ney apni aali sanad sey yehi hadees Fuleh bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) key shagrid Saeed bin Mansoor sey bhi bayan ki hai."
253,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs isliye ilm hasil karta hai ke be-ilm ( Awam ) sey behes karey ya ulama key muqabley mein fakhr ka izhar karey ya logon ki tawajjoh apni taraf mabzool kiraaey , wo jahannam mein jaeyga."
254,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ilm isliye hasil na karo ke ulama key muqabley mein fakhr ka izhar karo, na isliye ke kam-aql logon sey behes karo, na isliye ke majlis mein mumtaz maqam hasil karo. jisney aisa kya to (uskey liye) aag hai, aag hai."
255,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key kuch log Deen ka ilm hasil kerengey aur Quran padheingey. (phir) wo kahengey : hum hukmranon key paas jatey hain, unki duniya sey kuch hasil kar leingey aur apna Deen bacha kar alag ho jaeyngey. aisa nahin ho sakta. jis tarah Qatad (eik qism ka kaanton wala darkht) sey sirf kaantay hi hasil ho saktey hain (phal nahin) is tarah unkey paas ja kar kuch hasil nahin hoga siwaye. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad Muhammad bin sabaah (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : yani siwaye gunahon key ."
256,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : « جُبُّ الْحُزْن » sey Allah ki panah maango . Sahaba ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool « جُبُّ الْحُزْن » ( gham ka kunwaan) kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : jahannam ki eik wadi hai jis sey baqi jahannam bhi rozana chaar so dafa panah maangti hai. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is mein kon dakhil hoga ? farmaya : ye wadi un qaariyon key liye tayyar ki gaee hai jo apney aamal mein riyaakaari kartey hain, aur Allah key yahan sab sey qabilenafrat qurra wo hain jo hukmranon sey mulaqatein kartey hain. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey (hadees key Raavi ibne-Sireen) key barey mein Raavi ka tardeed bhi bayan kya ke wo Muhammad bin Sireen hai ya Anas bin Sireen."
257,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : agar ulama ilm ki hifazat kartey aur usey ehal logon key samney pesh kartey to (uski barkat sey) apney zamaney walon key sardar bin jatey. lekin unhoney ilm duniya daaron ki khidmat mein pesh kar diya taake uskey zariey sey un ki duniya mein sey kuch hasil kar lein , chunanche wo un ( ki nigahon ( mein be qadr ho gaey . mainey tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak suna hai : jis shakhs ney apney tamam tafakkurat ko eik hi fikr yani fikre-aakhirat mein dhaal liya, Allah usey duniya key tafakkurat sey bacha leta hai, aur jisey mukhtalif duniyawi maamlon ki fikr rehti hai aur wo un mein mashghool ho kar aakhirat ko bhula deta hai (Allah ko iski koi parwa nahin hoti ke kis wadi mein ja kar tabah hota hai.) Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid (abul-Hasan al-Qattan ney ye riwayat apni aali sanad sey ibne-Numair key doosrey do shagirdon abu-Bakar bin abi sheeba aur Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Numer sey bhi sabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan ki."
258,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney ghairullah key liye ilm talab kya ya us sey Allah key siwa kisi aur ka irada kya, usey chahiye ke apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley ."
259,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak suna hai : ilm ko is gharz sey hasil na karo ke ulama key muqabley mein fakhr ka izhar karo ya kam aql logon sey behes karo, ya logon ki tawajjoh apni taraf mabzool karo . jisney ye kaam kya, wo jahannami hai."
260,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney ilm isliye hasil kya ke uski wajeh sey ulama key muqabley mein fakhr karey ya kam aql logon sey behes karey ya logon ki tawajjoh apni taraf mabzool karey , to Allah Taala usey jahannam mein dakhil kerega."
261,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ko ilm (ka koi masla) yad ho, phir usney chupa liya, wo qiyamat key din is tarah aayega ke usey aag ki lagaam padi hogi . (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) abul-Hasan al-Qattan ney ye riwayat apni aali sanad sey Imaara bin Azan key doosrey shagrid abul-Waleed ki sanad sey bhi isi tarah bayan ki."
262,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qism hai Allah ki ! agar Allah Taala ki kitab ( Quran majeed) mein do aayaten na hoten to main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki koi hadees bayan na karta , yani agar ye aayaten na hoten : (إِنَّ الَّذِينَ يَكْتُمُونَ مَا أَنزلَ اللَّهُ مِنَ الْكِتَابِ وَيَشْتَرُونَ بِهِ ثَمَنًا قَلِيلا أُولَئِكَ مَا يَأْكُلُونَ فِي بُطُونِهِمْ إِلا النَّارَ وَلا يُكَلِّمُهُمُ اللَّهُ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ وَلا يُزَكِّيهِمْ وَلَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ O أُولَئِكَ الَّذِينَ اشْتَرَوُا الضَّلالَةَ بِالْهُدَى وَالْعَذَابَ بِالْمَغْفِرَةِ فَمَا أَصْبَرَهُمْ عَلَى النَّارِ )be shak jo log Allah ki utaari hui kitab chupatey hain aur usey thodi si qeemat par bechtey hain wo apney peton mein mehaz aag bhar rahey hain. qiyamat key din Allah Taala un sey kalam nahin kerega, na unhen pak kerega, aur unkey liye dardnak azab hai. ye log hain jinhoney hidayat key badley gumrahi ko aur bakhshish key badley azab ko kharid liya hai. ye log aag ka azab kis qadr bardasht karney waley hain."
263,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab ummat key pichley log pahlon par lanat karney lagen, us waqt jisney koi hadees chupai , usney Allah ki nazil karda chiz ko chupa liya ."
264,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai : aap ney farmaya : jis sey ilm ki koi baat daryaft ki gaee, phir usney isey chupaya , usey qiyamat key din aag ki lagaam di jaeygi ."
265,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney ilm ki koi aisi baat chupai jis sey Allah logon ko Deen key mamley mein faeyda pahunchata hai, usey qiyamat key din Allah Taala aag ki lagaam daleyga ."
266,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis sey ilm ka koi aisa masla puchha gaya jo usey malum tha, phir bhi usney isey chupaya , usey qiyamat key din aag ki lagaam dali jaeygi ."
